00:26:04,696 --> 00:26:07,324
你去西班牙女修道院找我幹嘛？
What were you doing in a Spanish convent，anyway？

390
00:26:07,499 --> 00:26:08,864
我弄錯了以為是妓院
Mistook it for a brothel. 

391
00:26:08,866 --> 00:26:10,229
走錯門了
Honest mistake. 

392
00:26:14,172 --> 00:26:14,989
他在這
There he is！

393
00:26:14,991 --> 00:26:15,799
在那
Over there！

394
00:26:34,225 --> 00:26:36,159
我們處於不利地位
We are at a disadvantage. 

395
00:26:36,294 --> 00:26:37,695
是說妳自己吧
Speak for yourself. 

396
00:26:37,697 --> 00:26:39,695
哪像某人只會冒充我
Unlike some who pretend to be，

397
00:26:39,864 --> 00:26:41,627
卻沒有我厲害
but cannot，in fact，hold a candle to，

398
00:26:41,766 --> 00:26:43,233
我才是傑克史派洛船長
I am Captain Jack Sparrow. 

399
00:27:20,438 --> 00:27:22,998
妳怎麼能說我利用了妳？
How can you say I used you？

400
00:27:23,141 --> 00:27:25,336
你明白的很
You know exactly how. 

401
00:27:25,477 --> 00:27:28,605
我知道，但妳怎麼能這麼說？
I know，but how can you say it？

402
00:27:33,251 --> 00:27:34,997
怎麼回事？
So，what is it？

403
00:27:34,999 --> 00:27:36,743
什麼怎麼回事？
What is what？

404
00:27:36,921 --> 00:27:38,411
青春之泉啊
About the Fountain. 

405
00:27:41,026 --> 00:27:42,050
你都知道什麼？
What do you know？

406
00:27:44,029 --> 00:27:45,621
妳不會是恰好有
You don't happen to be in possession

407
00:27:45,730 --> 00:27:48,995
龐塞德萊昂的兩隻銀杯吧？
of two silver chalices，circa Ponce de Leon？

408
00:27:49,701 --> 00:27:50,634
沒有
No. 

409
00:27:50,636 --> 00:27:51,566
我想也沒有
Thought not. 

410
00:27:51,703 --> 00:27:53,517
為什麼？
Why？

411
00:27:53,519 --> 00:27:55,332
我聽到一些說法
I hear stories. 

412
00:27:55,473 --> 00:27:57,304
謠傳
Rumors. 

413
00:27:57,409 --> 00:27:59,570
妳一定知道那個儀式
You are，of course，aware of the ritual. 

414
00:28:00,545 --> 00:28:01,637
對，我知道
Yes，I am. 

415
00:28:03,982 --> 00:28:05,347
是什麼儀式？
What is it？

416
00:28:05,349 --> 00:28:06,712
需要什麼？
What is required？

417
00:28:11,322 --> 00:28:13,313
一隻人魚，傑克
A mermaid，Jack. 

418
00:28:21,299 --> 00:28:22,698
你們搞錯了
There's been a mistake. 

419
00:28:22,834 --> 00:28:24,010
是無期徒刑
It's a life sentence，

420
00:28:24,350 --> 00:28:25,229
不是死刑
not death. 

421
00:28:25,361 --> 00:28:26,361
是無期！
Life！

422
00:28:31,776 --> 00:28:33,442
巴船長
Barbossa. 

423
00:28:33,444 --> 00:28:35,109
各位，謝謝你們
Thank you，gentlemen. 

424
00:28:35,246 --> 00:28:38,238
我想你會綁絞繩吧
I trust you can tie a noose. 

425
00:28:38,383 --> 00:28:39,782
這是很困難的事
That's a hard thing，

426
00:28:39,918 --> 00:28:42,910
逼一個人綁自己的絞繩
forcing a man to twis this own hanging rope. 

427
00:28:43,755 --> 00:28:46,588
你必須為你的行為付出代價
You must lie in your bed the way you made it. 

428
00:28:48,426 --> 00:28:49,791
你是怎麼了？
What's happened to you？

429
00:28:49,928 --> 00:28:51,646
傑克史派洛呢？
Where be Jack Sparrow？

430
00:28:51,648 --> 00:28:53,364
他逃走了
He escaped. 

431
00:28:53,465 --> 00:28:54,932
吉卜，我在趕時間
I'm on a tight schedule，Gibbs. 

432
00:28:55,066 --> 00:28:57,432
天佑號天一亮就啟航
The HMS Providence sets sail at first light. 

433
00:28:57,569 --> 00:28:59,730
如果你不想屍體被吊在這裡
If you do not care to watch it hanging here dead，

434
00:28:59,871 --> 00:29:01,896
滿嘴都是蒼蠅...
with a mouth full of flies...

435
00:29:03,541 --> 00:29:05,168
...現在就說
...speak now. 

436
00:29:06,911 --> 00:29:08,156
帶上我吧
Take me with you. 

437
00:29:08,157 --> 00:29:09,546
去哪兒都行...
Any point of the compass...

438
00:29:09,547 --> 00:29:11,965
吉卜，帶你去哪呀？
Take you where，Gibbs？

439
00:29:11,966 --> 00:29:14,382
青春之泉？是嗎？
The Fountain？Aye？

440
00:29:14,486 --> 00:29:17,512
傑克也要去那兒吧？
Is that where Jack be headed？

441
00:29:17,689 --> 00:29:21,716
吉卜，你能給我什麼？
Have you anything you can offer me，Gibbs？

442
00:29:21,826 --> 00:29:23,384
什麼都沒有？
Anything at all？

443
00:29:25,163 --> 00:29:26,909
我說話算話
Upon me naked word，

444
00:29:26,910 --> 00:29:28,655
你看不到日出了
you'll not see the dawn. 

445
00:29:36,708 --> 00:29:38,437
拿過來
Hand it over. 

446
00:29:43,181 --> 00:29:44,328
你這笨蛋！
You fool！

447
00:29:44,330 --> 00:29:45,479
我正好有足夠時間
I had just enough time

448
00:29:45,617 --> 00:29:48,108
研究這些陰間的符號
to study those infernal circles. 

449
00:29:48,253 --> 00:29:50,568
每條路線，每個目的地
Every route，every destination. 

450
00:29:50,570 --> 00:29:52,883
全都在…這
All safe... in here. 

451
00:29:54,392 --> 00:29:58,419
吉卜先生，歡迎加入皇家海軍
Welcome back to His Majesty's navy，Master Gibbs. 

452
00:30:11,509 --> 00:30:13,500
起床了，水手！
Show a leg，sailor！

453
00:30:13,645 --> 00:30:14,873
是，長官
Aye，sir. 

454
00:30:16,414 --> 00:30:17,711
什麼？
What？

455
00:30:17,849 --> 00:30:19,450
這誤會大了
There's been a horrible mistake. 

456
00:30:19,452 --> 00:30:21,046
繼續走
Keep moving. 

457
00:30:22,554 --> 00:30:24,039
我不應該在這裡
I'm not supposed to be here. 

458
00:30:24,041 --> 00:30:25,523
很多人在船上醒來
Many a man's woken up at sea，

459
00:30:25,657 --> 00:30:27,591
都搞不清楚狀況
no idea what，when，wherefore or why. 

460
00:30:27,759 --> 00:30:28,874
不記得前一晚
No memory of the night afore，

461
00:30:28,876 --> 00:30:29,989
在哪簽了什麼合同
whence he signed up

462
00:30:30,128 --> 00:30:31,652
還把錢通通拿去買醉
and drank away all his bonus money. 

463
00:30:31,796 --> 00:30:33,787
不，老兄，你不明白
No，no，no. You don't understand，mate. 

464
00:30:33,898 --> 00:30:35,115
我是傑克史派洛船長
I'm Captain Jack Sparrow. 

465
00:30:35,117 --> 00:30:36,332
獨此一家，如假包換
The original. The only. 

466
00:30:36,467 --> 00:30:37,747
我是石頭，幸會了
Scrum，and the pleasure's all mine. 

467
00:30:37,749 --> 00:30:39,027
繼續走
Now，keep moving. 

468
00:30:47,545 --> 00:30:49,012
石頭
Scrum. 

469
00:30:49,147 --> 00:30:51,377
靠過來
Get your elbows in！

470
00:30:53,885 --> 00:30:55,750
為什麼那有一個玻璃棺？
Why is there a glass coffin？

471
00:30:55,887 --> 00:30:58,355
看來像我管的？
Do I look like a man in charge？

472
00:30:58,489 --> 00:30:59,957
我在哪裡？
Where am I？

473
00:30:59,959 --> 00:31:01,424
抱歉，史派洛船長
'Scuse me，Captain Sparrow，sir. 

474
00:31:01,559 --> 00:31:03,220
我很榮幸歡迎你登上
I be right honoredto welcome you aboard

475
00:31:03,361 --> 00:31:04,994
臭名狼藉的
our world-renowned vessel of infamy，

476
00:31:04,996 --> 00:31:06,626
安妮王后復仇號
Queen Anne's Revenge. 

477
00:31:10,034 --> 00:31:11,695
黑鬍子的船
Blackbeard. 

478
00:31:28,052 --> 00:31:29,917
幹活
Work！

479
00:31:33,725 --> 00:31:35,591
他是一個奇怪的傢伙
He's a curious one. 

480
00:31:35,593 --> 00:31:37,454
他是活死人
He's been zombiefied. 

481
00:31:37,456 --> 00:31:38,728
啥？

482
00:31:38,730 --> 00:31:40,254
活死人
Zombiefied. 

483
00:31:40,398 --> 00:31:42,144
黑鬍子幹的
Blackbeard's doing. 

484
00:31:42,146 --> 00:31:43,890
每個頭兒都是
All the officers are the same. 

485
00:31:44,035 --> 00:31:45,764
好讓他們更順從
Makes 'em more compliant. 

486
00:31:47,038 --> 00:31:49,006
而且脾氣一樣壞
And perpetually ill-tempered. 

487
00:31:50,708 --> 00:31:52,005
快點，用力擦洗
Come on. Scrub. 

488
00:31:52,007 --> 00:31:53,302
是
Yeah. 

489
00:32:00,385 --> 00:32:04,014
拉！拉！用力拉！
Pull！Pull！Pull！

490
00:32:08,559 --> 00:32:11,119
航行了五天，至少
Five days underway，at least. 

491
00:32:11,262 --> 00:32:15,096
對，你從海水味道聞出來的？
Aye. You can tell thatby the smell of the sea？

492
00:32:15,233 --> 00:32:16,962
是船員的臭味
Smell of the crew. 

493
00:32:20,538 --> 00:32:23,632
喂，那可憐的混帳幹了什麼？
Oi. What did that poor sod do？

494
00:32:23,775 --> 00:32:25,800
我該怎樣才不會這樣？
And how can I make sure to not？

495
00:32:25,944 --> 00:32:28,276
他喔？是虔誠教徒
Him？Churchly fellow. 

496
00:32:28,413 --> 00:32:30,438
老唸著萬能的主啊
Always going on about the Lord Almighty. 

497
00:32:30,581 --> 00:32:32,310
宗教狂熱份子在這艘船上？
Bible-thumper on this ship？

498
00:32:32,450 --> 00:32:34,350
他以前是傳教士
A missionary is his story. 

499
00:32:34,485 --> 00:32:37,249
我聽說他是在一次劫掠中被抓來
What I heard was he got captured in a raid. 

500
00:32:37,355 --> 00:32:40,256
船上其他人全被殺了，除了他
Rest of the ship got killed，but not 'im. 

501
00:32:40,358 --> 00:32:41,689
大副不肯殺死他
First mate wouldn't let it happen

502
00:32:41,826 --> 00:32:44,522
因為他信主
on account of his premier standing with the Lord. 

503
00:32:44,662 --> 00:32:46,865
大副以她的生命
A first mate sticking her neck 

504
00:32:46,867 --> 00:32:49,065
替囚犯求情
out for some prisoner. 

505
00:32:49,233 --> 00:32:50,825
那是你不能理解的
That you don't see. 

506
00:32:50,969 --> 00:32:53,665
「她」？大副是「女的」？
「Her」？First mate is a「her」？

507
00:32:53,805 --> 00:32:55,033
回去幹活！
Back to work！

508
00:33:04,349 --> 00:33:06,613
穩穩地保持航向
Steady as she goes. 

509
00:33:20,832 --> 00:33:23,017
妳是個無情的
You are a ruthless，

510
00:33:23,019 --> 00:33:25,201
卑鄙的，超級難搞的壞蛋
soulless，cross-grained cur. 

511
00:33:25,336 --> 00:33:27,082
我跟你說過我有一艘船
I told you I had a ship. 

512
00:33:27,084 --> 00:33:28,828
不對，是黑鬍子有一艘船
No，Blackbeard has a ship，

513
00:33:28,973 --> 00:33:31,771
妳害我變成囚犯
upon which I am now imprisoned. 

514
00:33:31,943 --> 00:33:33,911
傑克，我們辦得到的
We can do this，Jack. 

515
00:33:34,045 --> 00:33:36,343
青春之泉
The Fountain of Youth，

516
00:33:36,344 --> 00:33:38,641
你不也一直想找到
like you always wanted. 

517
00:33:38,750 --> 00:33:40,033
黑鬍子
Blackbeard. 

518
00:33:40,034 --> 00:33:41,315
愛德華汀奇
Edward Teach. 

519
00:33:41,317 --> 00:33:43,881
所有海盜都怕的海盜
The pirate all pirates fear. 

520
00:33:44,022 --> 00:33:46,183
有空就玩玩死人復活
Resurrector of the dead in his spare time. 

521
00:33:46,324 --> 00:33:47,758
他會聽我的
He will listen to me. 

522
00:33:47,760 --> 00:33:49,191
他誰也不會聽
He listens to no one. 

523
00:33:49,327 --> 00:33:52,228
也許會聽他親生女兒的？
Maybe to his own daughter？

524
00:33:54,766 --> 00:33:57,701
女兒…親生女兒？
Daughter as in... beget by？

525
00:33:58,569 --> 00:34:00,486
失散很久
Long-lost. 

526
00:34:00,487 --> 00:34:02,403
最近才相認
Recently found. 

527
00:34:02,540 --> 00:34:06,374
全心全意愛她的老爸
Who loves her dear papa with all her soul. 

528
00:34:06,511 --> 00:34:07,541
他信這套鬼話？
He bought that？

529
00:34:07,543 --> 00:34:08,570
我說服了他
I sold that. 

530
00:34:16,020 --> 00:34:17,817
那麼找青春之泉是為了他
Then it's the Fountain of Youth for him，

531
00:34:17,989 --> 00:34:19,456
或者是為了你們
or him and you，

532
00:34:19,457 --> 00:34:20,922
不是為了我們
not you and me. 

533
00:34:20,992 --> 00:34:23,051
不，傑克，最棒的是
No，Jack，that's the best part. 

534
00:34:23,194 --> 00:34:25,253
他就快要死了
He will be dead. 

535
00:34:26,564 --> 00:34:28,964
妳要親手殺了他？
You'll be handling that part yourself，then？

536
00:34:29,100 --> 00:34:31,364
有一個預言
There is a prophecy. 

537
00:34:31,469 --> 00:34:33,699
也許你不相信超自然現象
Maybe you don't believein the supernatural. 

538
00:34:33,805 --> 00:34:34,960
喔，不
Oh，no，no. 

539
00:34:34,962 --> 00:34:36,296
這我倒是看過一兩次
I've seen a thing or two. 

540
00:34:38,876 --> 00:34:42,835
這個預言是這樣的：
The prophecy is this:

541
00:34:43,014 --> 00:34:46,814
黑鬍子兩周內將會死亡
Blackbeard will meet his death within a fortnight

542
00:34:46,951 --> 00:34:50,409
死在一個獨腿者的手上
at the hands of a one-legged man. 

543
00:34:50,555 --> 00:34:52,750
所以他需要青春之泉
That's why he needs the Fountain，Jack. 

544
00:35:09,073 --> 00:35:11,837
吉卜先生，我們沒有地圖
Master Gibbs，short we are a map. 

545
00:35:11,976 --> 00:35:13,523
也許你該好心
Perhaps you'd be so kindas 

546
00:35:13,523 --> 00:35:15,070
給我們一個航向
to provide us an heading. 

547
00:35:18,850 --> 00:35:20,943
麻煩倒杯酒給我
Be a gem and pour me a gulper. 

548
00:35:21,085 --> 00:35:22,803
不行，我們是私掠船
Nay. We be privateers， 

549
00:35:22,804 --> 00:35:24,521
不是海盜，吉卜先生
not pirates，Master Gibbs.

550
00:35:24,655 --> 00:35:26,782
我們奉國王陛下之名行事
And in the king's name，we behave as such. 

551
00:35:26,924 --> 00:35:29,757
遵命，船長
Aye，Captain. 

552
00:35:33,164 --> 00:35:35,962
吉卜，我們是在正確的航線上嗎？
Be we on the proper course，Gibbs？

553
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:38,398
對，是正確的
Aye，it be proper. 

554
00:35:38,400 --> 00:35:40,696
那就是證明
There's your proof. 

555
00:35:47,211 --> 00:35:48,508
西班牙艦隊
The Spaniard. 

556
00:35:50,081 --> 00:35:53,236
全員注意，戰鬥位置
All hands！Battle stations！

557
00:35:53,238 --> 00:35:54,814
航向上風
Get to windward！

558
00:35:54,952 --> 00:35:56,482
全員注意，航向上風
All hands，windward！

559
00:35:56,484 --> 00:35:58,012
加固兩點
Harden up two points！

560
00:35:58,156 --> 00:35:59,874
兩點
Two points！

561
00:35:59,876 --> 00:36:01,592
砲手解開大砲
Cast loose the cannons！

562
00:36:05,563 --> 00:36:07,446
槍手，各就各位
Gunners，take posts！

563
00:36:07,448 --> 00:36:09,329
就位，槍手待命，長官
Take position！Gunners ready，sir！

564
00:36:09,467 --> 00:36:11,401
大砲解開，填彈
Out！Thrust！

565
00:36:11,403 --> 00:36:13,335
等待命令
Await orders. 

566
00:36:15,439 --> 00:36:16,804
穩住
Steady！

567
00:36:18,142 --> 00:36:19,734
填好砲彈，等待命令，長官
Guns armed，awaiting orders，sir. 

568
00:36:25,516 --> 00:36:29,077
長官，命令，長官？
Sir. Orders，sir？

569
00:36:35,693 --> 00:36:38,423
他甚至都沒有轉動他的頭
He never so much as turned his head. 

570
00:36:38,563 --> 00:36:40,428
青春之泉才是目標
The Fountain is the prize. 

571
00:36:40,565 --> 00:36:42,380
看來他們不想浪費時間
It appears we be not even worth the time 

572
00:36:42,381 --> 00:36:44,194
擊沉我們
it'd take to sink us. 

573
00:36:44,335 --> 00:36:46,286
我們已經落後了
And now we've fallen behind. 

574
00:36:46,288 --> 00:36:48,237
全員注意，全速前進
All hands，make more sail！

575
00:36:48,372 --> 00:36:50,932
全員注意，全速前進
All hands，more sail！

576
00:36:51,075 --> 00:36:54,408
讓我們乘風破浪吧
Ride hard between wind and tide！

577
00:37:04,388 --> 00:37:07,983
各位，我要說的可是叛變
The topic，gentlemen，is mutiny. 

578
00:37:08,759 --> 00:37:10,556
最可怕的叛變
Mutiny most foul. 

579
00:37:10,695 --> 00:37:13,000
是呀，我是來當傑克史派洛的船員
Aye. I signed up to sail under Jack Sparrow，

580
00:37:13,002 --> 00:37:14,222
不是冒牌船長
not some pretender. 

581
00:37:14,365 --> 00:37:15,627
而且還是個女的
And a lady，at that. 

582
00:37:15,766 --> 00:37:17,961
也沒人提到船上有活死人
And mention was failed to be made of this uncanny crew. 

583
00:37:18,102 --> 00:37:20,468
我怕得腿都軟了
Make my toes curl，they do. 

584
00:37:20,605 --> 00:37:22,135
我拿到了
I got 'em.

585
00:37:22,137 --> 00:37:23,665
全部
All of them. 

586
00:37:23,841 --> 00:37:24,808
幹得好
Well done. 

587
00:37:24,810 --> 00:37:25,775
好樣的
Good lad. 

588
00:37:25,910 --> 00:37:28,344
我說，黑鬍子
On to it，then. Blackbeard. 

589
00:37:28,512 --> 00:37:29,729
有什麼習慣？
What are his habits？

590
00:37:29,731 --> 00:37:30,946
他多半都待在船長室
Stays mostly to his cabin. 

591
00:37:31,082 --> 00:37:33,880
沒錯，都待在船長室
That's right，mostly to his cabin. 

592
00:37:33,985 --> 00:37:35,600
沒錯，但是當他出來...
Yes，but when he comes out...

593
00:37:35,602 --> 00:37:37,216
他從來都不出來
He don't really come out. 

594
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:40,555
他總是會出來吧
He must come out sometime. 

595
00:37:41,425 --> 00:37:43,620
並沒有
Not really，no. 

596
00:37:45,463 --> 00:37:47,158
有人和他航海過？
Any of you sail with him before？

597
00:37:47,298 --> 00:37:48,032
沒，沒有
No，no. 

598
00:37:48,034 --> 00:37:48,765
我從來沒有
I've never. 

599
00:37:48,899 --> 00:37:49,923
絕對沒有
Definitely not. 

600
00:37:50,067 --> 00:37:52,000
有人看過他？
Any of you seen him before？

601
00:37:52,002 --> 00:37:53,935
並沒有，沒有
Not really，no. 

602
00:37:55,539 --> 00:37:56,620
他待在船長室
Stays to his cabin，

603
00:37:56,622 --> 00:37:57,700
沒人和他航海
no one sailed with him，

604
00:37:57,875 --> 00:37:59,900
沒人見過他...
no one's seen him...

605
00:38:00,077 --> 00:38:01,645
各位，好消息
Good news，gentlemen. 

606
00:38:01,647 --> 00:38:03,212
這不是黑鬍子的船
This is not Blackbeard's ship. 

607
00:38:03,214 --> 00:38:05,147
這不是安妮王后復仇號
This is not the Queen Anne's Revenge. 

608
00:38:05,149 --> 00:38:07,174
不對，這是安妮王后復仇號
No，this be the Queen Anne's Revenge，right enough. 

609
00:38:07,318 --> 00:38:08,785
你怎麼知道？
How do you know？

610
00:38:08,919 --> 00:38:10,552
我看過船名
I've seen the name，

611
00:38:10,554 --> 00:38:12,184
就在船尾
on the back of the ship. 

612
00:38:15,426 --> 00:38:20,386
各位，各位夥伴...
Gentlemen，sirs，fellow conscriptees...

613
00:38:22,133 --> 00:38:24,260
...你們都被騙了
...you have been monstrously deceived. 

614
00:38:24,368 --> 00:38:27,350
我們被耍了？
We are decepted，then？

615
00:38:27,352 --> 00:38:28,532
沒錯
Yes. 

616
00:38:28,673 --> 00:38:31,608
你們都不知道目的地吧
You've nay been informed of a destination. 

617
00:38:31,709 --> 00:38:33,870
死亡就擺在我們面前了
Death lies before us

618
00:38:34,011 --> 00:38:36,429
因為我們正航向
as we sail 

619
00:38:36,430 --> 00:38:38,846
青春之泉
for the Fountain of Youth. 

620
00:38:40,651 --> 00:38:42,346
情況不妙啊，夥計們
It would be a sorry plight，mates. 

621
00:38:42,486 --> 00:38:44,898
我們死定了
Death，for certain. 

622
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:46,616
那兒是幽靈的花園
The garden of darkened souls. 

623
00:38:46,724 --> 00:38:48,407
我們的葬生之地
Untimely our ends will be. 

624
00:38:48,409 --> 00:38:50,091
除非...
Unless...

625
00:38:50,261 --> 00:38:52,752
...我們搶下這艘船
...we take the ship. 

626
00:38:54,065 --> 00:38:57,626
我們搶下這艘船，現在！
We take the ship，then. Now！

627
00:39:01,839 --> 00:39:03,363
快去啊
Go on，then. 

628
00:39:04,141 --> 00:39:05,455
快幫忙，水手們！
Help me，shipmates！

629
00:39:05,457 --> 00:39:06,769
給他們武器！
Give it to 'em！

630
00:39:06,944 --> 00:39:08,059
起來！船是我們的！
Wake up！It's ours！

631
00:39:08,061 --> 00:39:09,174
快一點！
Come on！

632
00:39:09,313 --> 00:39:10,974
起來！讓開！
Get up！Off your backside！

633
00:39:12,516 --> 00:39:13,699
你們起來！
Get off your fannies！

634
00:39:13,701 --> 00:39:14,882
給他們武器！
Take it to them，lads！

635
00:39:15,019 --> 00:39:16,850
快幫忙！戰鬥！
Help me！Fight！

636
00:39:30,401 --> 00:39:31,800
傑克
Jack. 

637
00:39:33,437 --> 00:39:35,752
如果這是夢
If this is a dream，

638
00:39:35,754 --> 00:39:38,067
你可以留著劍和靴子
you can keep the sword and boots on. 

639
00:39:40,211 --> 00:39:41,474
如果不是...
If it's not...

640
00:39:41,476 --> 00:39:42,736
這當然是夢
It's a dream. 

641
00:39:48,352 --> 00:39:49,410
不，才怪！
No，it's not！

642
00:39:50,721 --> 00:39:52,522
我覺得該好心先給妳警告
I thought I should give you fair warning，

643
00:39:52,524 --> 00:39:54,323
我們要搶這艘船
we're taking the ship. 

644
00:39:54,325 --> 00:39:55,815
這不是個人恩怨
Nothing personal. 

645
00:39:56,894 --> 00:39:58,794
這對妳可能比較好...
Think you might be better off if you just...

646
00:40:00,431 --> 00:40:01,762
...妳只要待著別插手
...stay out of it. 

647
00:40:25,356 --> 00:40:26,653
礙事

648
00:40:48,145 --> 00:40:49,544
可惡！
Wretch！

649
00:41:19,176 --> 00:41:21,167
是當夥伴還是當敵人！
You're either with us or against us！

650
00:41:21,312 --> 00:41:22,479
我不支持你們
I am not with you，

651
00:41:22,481 --> 00:41:23,645
也不反對你們！
neither am I against you！

652
00:41:23,647 --> 00:41:25,012
他到底要怎麼樣？
Can he do that？

653
00:41:25,149 --> 00:41:28,175
他本來就沒有什麼自己的立場
He's religious. I believe it's required. 

654
00:41:33,491 --> 00:41:35,150
奮戰到底吧
Fight to the bitter end，

655
00:41:35,152 --> 00:41:36,824
你們這群傻蛋！
you cack-handed deck apes！

656
00:41:48,639 --> 00:41:49,839
抓住他
Take him，men. 

657
00:41:49,841 --> 00:41:51,039
把他綁牢了！
Tie him down tight！

658
00:42:05,789 --> 00:42:07,518
船是我們的了！
The ship is ours！

659
00:42:36,353 --> 00:42:38,583
各位
Gentlemen. 

660
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:49,522
我被搞糊塗了
I be placed in a bewilderment. 

661
00:42:49,633 --> 00:42:51,965
我正在
There I were，

662
00:42:51,966 --> 00:42:54,297
休息著
resting，

663
00:42:54,438 --> 00:42:55,838
然後突然間
and upon a sudden，

664
00:42:55,840 --> 00:42:59,102
聽到甲板傳來吵鬧聲
I hear an ungodly row on deck. 

665
00:43:02,179 --> 00:43:04,113
水手們擅離崗位
Sailors abandon their posts

666
00:43:04,248 --> 00:43:06,773
沒有命令，未經許可
without orders，without leave. 

667
00:43:07,885 --> 00:43:11,116
幹粗活的水手
Men before the mast，

668
00:43:11,255 --> 00:43:13,655
想要聯手搶下這艘船
taking the ship for themselves. 

669
00:43:15,392 --> 00:43:17,690
那算什麼呀，大副？
What be that，First Mate？

670
00:43:17,861 --> 00:43:19,278
叛變，船長
Mutiny，Captain. 

671
00:43:19,280 --> 00:43:20,694
再說一次？
Again？

672
00:43:20,864 --> 00:43:22,349
叛變！
Mutiny！

673
00:43:22,351 --> 00:43:23,833
是啊
Aye. 

674
00:43:24,401 --> 00:43:26,096
叛變
Mutiny. 

675
00:43:28,606 --> 00:43:32,042
叛變者的下場是什麼？
And what fate befalls mutineers？

676
00:43:32,209 --> 00:43:35,701
大家都知道答案了，對吧？
Now，we know the answer to that，do we not？

677
00:43:35,879 --> 00:43:39,440
你們這是自尋死路！
Mutineers hang！

678
00:44:29,266 --> 00:44:30,995
船長，我要報告有人叛變
Captain，I wish to report a mutiny. 

679
00:44:31,903 --> 00:44:34,289
我能扳著指頭數出來，一個個報給你聽
I can name fingers and point names. 

680
00:44:34,271 --> 00:44:35,738
用不著，史派洛先生
No need，Mr.Sparrow. 

681
00:44:35,873 --> 00:44:37,489
他們是嘍囉
They are sheep. 

682
00:44:37,491 --> 00:44:39,104
你，才是主腦
You，their shepherd. 

683
00:44:44,014 --> 00:44:45,362
我有提過
Have I mentioned，sir，

684
00:44:45,364 --> 00:44:46,710
你女兒有多美嗎？
what a lovely daughter you have？

685
00:44:47,351 --> 00:44:49,785
那她就是你死前最後的美景了
A fitting last sight for a doomed soul. 

686
00:44:49,953 --> 00:44:51,153
別忘了，父親
Remember，Father. 

687
00:44:51,155 --> 00:44:52,353
我們需要他
We need him. 

688
00:44:52,489 --> 00:44:54,089
如果我不隔幾天就殺個人
If I don't kill a man every now and then，

689
00:44:54,091 --> 00:44:55,089
大家就會忘了我是誰
they forget who I am. 

690
00:44:55,091 --> 00:44:56,525
懦夫！
Coward！

691
00:44:58,162 --> 00:45:00,392
他們不會忘記
They do not forget. 

692
00:45:00,497 --> 00:45:02,863
你的船員視你如惡棍
Your crew sees you for the miscreant you are. 

693
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:05,332
是個懦夫，不管你殺多少人
A coward，no matter how many you slay. 

694
00:45:05,436 --> 00:45:07,870
我又被搞糊塗了
Twice in one day，I find myself in a bewilderment. 

695
00:45:08,005 --> 00:45:10,132
你沒有被搞糊塗，你是害怕
You are not bewildered，you are afraid. 

696
00:45:10,841 --> 00:45:11,990
你不敢走向正義
You dare not walk the path of righteousness，

697
00:45:11,991 --> 00:45:13,139
走向光明之路
the way of the light. 

698
00:45:13,310 --> 00:45:17,679
不對，我沒那麼複雜
No，sir. The truth is it be much simpler than all that.

699
00:45:17,681 --> 00:45:19,378
我是個壞人
I am a bad man. 

700
00:45:19,380 --> 00:45:20,582
那，也是
That，too. 

701
00:45:20,718 --> 00:45:22,709
我也許也得殺了你，牧師
I might have to kill you too，catechist. 

702
00:45:22,853 --> 00:45:23,900
不行！
No！

703
00:45:23,902 --> 00:45:25,447
就像她拉丁媽媽
All Latin blood like her mother. 

704
00:45:25,589 --> 00:45:27,682
父親，求求你
Father，I beg you. 

705
00:45:27,791 --> 00:45:29,046
我又來了
There I be again，

706
00:45:29,047 --> 00:45:31,557
老忘記傳教士為什麼在這裡
forgetting why the missionary is here. 

707
00:45:31,695 --> 00:45:36,098
是我女兒想救贖我僅存的靈魂
My daughter fears for my soul，or what's left of it. 

708
00:45:37,101 --> 00:45:40,764
妳真的想救贖我嗎，我的孩子？
You truly wish to save me，my child？

709
00:45:40,904 --> 00:45:42,838
每個靈魂都會被救贖
Every soul can be saved. 

710
00:45:43,907 --> 00:45:45,772
真的嗎，年輕的牧師？
Be that true，young cleric？

711
00:45:45,909 --> 00:45:46,909
是的
Yes. 

712
00:45:46,911 --> 00:45:49,606
我看雖然救贖你是有一點風險
Though you I sees a bit of a long shot. 

713
00:45:50,614 --> 00:45:52,594
我仍然為這地獄船上
Still，I pray for every unfortunate 

714
00:45:52,595 --> 00:45:54,573
每個不幸的靈魂祈禱
soulon this hell-bound vessel. 

715
00:45:57,121 --> 00:45:59,783
妳用妳的信仰解除了我的武裝
You disarm me with your faith. 

716
00:46:01,158 --> 00:46:02,625
現在是八點！
Eight bells！

717
00:46:02,760 --> 00:46:05,752
是哪個不幸的靈魂守瞭望台？
Which of you unfortunate soulsstood watch？

718
00:46:05,896 --> 00:46:08,376
是我，是我在守望
I did. I stood watch. 

719
00:46:08,378 --> 00:46:10,856
砲手
Gunner. 

720
00:46:16,240 --> 00:46:17,639
是你？
You？

721
00:46:18,308 --> 00:46:19,935
是
Aye. 

722
00:46:20,477 --> 00:46:22,274
好吧
Aye. 

723
00:46:22,412 --> 00:46:24,403
廚子
The cook. 

724
00:46:24,515 --> 00:46:27,416
太好了，降下長艇！
Perfect. Lower the longboat！

725
00:46:32,656 --> 00:46:34,647
掉頭！
Bring her about！

726
00:46:46,203 --> 00:46:47,716
你為什麼要這樣做？
Why do you do this？

727
00:46:47,718 --> 00:46:49,229
叛變，我們的法律是清楚的
Mutiny. Our laws be clear. 

728
00:46:49,406 --> 00:46:51,670
我們的法律允許船長法外施恩
Our laws allow the Captain to show leniency. 

729
00:46:51,809 --> 00:46:54,437
我給過他機會決定他的命運
I have given this mana chance to determine his fate，

730
00:46:54,545 --> 00:46:56,240
不是每個人都有的
a gift not afforded to all. 

731
00:47:05,355 --> 00:47:06,822
喔，現在你
Oh，you now. 

732
00:47:08,125 --> 00:47:10,859
有機會來顯現你的祈禱的價值了
Chance to show the worth of your prayers. 

733
00:47:10,861 --> 00:47:14,922
祈禱他脫離…邪惡？
Pray he be delivered from... evil？

734
00:47:23,240 --> 00:47:24,605
瞄準目標！
Course made！

735
00:47:24,775 --> 00:47:26,606
住手，給他機會，也給你自己...
Stop. Give that man a chance. Give yourself a...

736
00:47:52,336 --> 00:47:55,070
知道我在什麼時候最接近造物主？
You know when I feel closest to our Maker？

737
00:47:55,072 --> 00:47:57,070
在我看到苦難，痛苦和悲傷的時候
When I see suffering，pain and anguish. 

738
00:47:57,074 --> 00:47:59,599
這時祂才會顯現真正的意圖
That's when the true design of this world is revealed. 

739
00:47:59,743 --> 00:48:03,440
我看到是祂在苦難和悲劇發生時
And I see it revealed when in times of hardship and tragedy，

740
00:48:03,580 --> 00:48:05,878
才對需要的人施予仁慈和憐憫
kindness and compassion are shown to those in need. 

741
00:48:06,016 --> 00:48:08,416
也許你該祈禱他不受傷害，是吧？
Perhaps you should pray for him to be unharmed，yes？

742
00:48:08,552 --> 00:48:09,650
他還有機會...
Please，there's still hope...

743
00:48:09,652 --> 00:48:10,747
再開砲！
Again！

744
00:48:23,500 --> 00:48:26,060
其實我對青春之泉毫無興趣
I actually have no interest in the Fountain whatsoever，

745
00:48:26,203 --> 00:48:28,068
如果你心意已定
so，if your heart is set，

746
00:48:28,205 --> 00:48:30,400
那我就任你處置
you may drop me off anywhere you like. 

747
00:48:30,540 --> 00:48:32,303
舵手，可以了
That'll be all，Quartermaster. 

748
00:48:35,312 --> 00:48:37,058
你說的話像霧一樣
Your words surround you like fog 

749
00:48:37,059 --> 00:48:38,804
讓我看不透
and make you hard to see. 

750
00:48:38,949 --> 00:48:42,783
你呢，強大的黑鬍子？
And what of you，the mighty Blackbeard？

751
00:48:42,920 --> 00:48:44,302
聽說你被砍頭
Beheaded they say. 

752
00:48:44,304 --> 00:48:47,574
但你的身體還繞著你的船游三圈
Still，your body swam three times around your ship， 

753
00:48:47,576 --> 00:48:49,292
然後爬上船去
then climbed back onboard. 

754
00:48:49,426 --> 00:48:50,723
而現在你好好的
And here you are，

755
00:48:50,724 --> 00:48:52,020
卻怕得要命
running scared. 

756
00:48:52,663 --> 00:48:54,381
怕得要命
Scared. 

757
00:48:54,383 --> 00:48:56,099
要找青春之泉
To the Fountain. 

758
00:48:56,233 --> 00:48:59,259
舵手有預知能力
The Quartermaster sees things before they happen. 

759
00:48:59,403 --> 00:49:01,560
他預知我的死亡
He has foreseen my death，

760
00:49:01,562 --> 00:49:03,897
所以命運開口了
and so the fates have spoken. 

761
00:49:04,007 --> 00:49:06,373
我的命運已經決定
The threads of destiny woven. 

762
00:49:06,543 --> 00:49:09,478
你太高估命運的力量了
You have a ridiculously high regard for fate，mate. 

763
00:49:09,613 --> 00:49:10,427
那你呢？
And you？

764
00:49:10,429 --> 00:49:11,240
我？
Me？

765
00:49:11,348 --> 00:49:13,498
預知命運我是懷疑的...
I'm skeptical of predicting any future... 

766
00:49:13,500 --> 00:49:15,648
包括我自己
which includes me. 

767
00:49:15,786 --> 00:49:18,687
反抗命運是件傻事
It'd be foolish to battle fate，

768
00:49:18,689 --> 00:49:21,588
但我想冒這個險
but I'd be tempted to cheat it. 

769
00:49:21,692 --> 00:49:23,143
我會找到青春之泉
I will reach the Fountain. 

770
00:49:23,145 --> 00:49:24,593
你會帶我去
You will lead me. 

771
00:49:27,030 --> 00:49:29,027
那把刀和你搞的
That knife will serve you no better than  

772
00:49:29,028 --> 00:49:31,023
叛變一樣沒用
the mutiny you devised. 

773
00:49:31,168 --> 00:49:32,965
叛變很有用
Mutiny served me well. 

774
00:49:33,103 --> 00:49:35,037
不是讓我見到你了
It gained me an audience with you. 

775
00:49:37,040 --> 00:49:38,268
是啊
Aye. 

776
00:49:39,676 --> 00:49:41,473
我要警告你
To warn you. 

777
00:49:42,446 --> 00:49:44,004
注意你的大副
Regarding your first mate，

778
00:49:44,147 --> 00:49:47,048
她並不是她說的那個人
who pretends to be persons she is not. 

779
00:49:47,651 --> 00:49:48,675
繼續說
Do tell. 

780
00:49:51,254 --> 00:49:53,051
她不是你的女兒
She is not your daughter. 

781
00:49:56,326 --> 00:49:59,386
你膽敢這麼說我的親生骨肉？
You dare to speak thusly of my flesh and blood？

782
00:49:59,529 --> 00:50:04,057
那女人是個高明的騙徒
Sir，the woman is consummate in the art of deception. 

783
00:50:04,201 --> 00:50:05,661
我很清楚
I know. 

784
00:50:05,663 --> 00:50:07,162
是我不小心
As I mostly unwittingly 

785
00:50:07,163 --> 00:50:08,661
讓她走上這條路
set her on her wicked path. 

786
00:50:08,805 --> 00:50:11,320
雖然我不能說
Though I cannot claim credit for her  

787
00:50:11,321 --> 00:50:13,843
她的天賦是我教的
existing abundance of natural talent. 

788
00:50:15,846 --> 00:50:18,337
安潔莉卡，我鍾愛的女兒
Angelica. My beloved daughter，

789
00:50:18,482 --> 00:50:21,076
我這輩子做過最好的事
the one true good thing I have done in this life，

790
00:50:21,218 --> 00:50:22,549
而你卻自稱你教壞了她？
and you claim to be the one who corrupted her？

791
00:50:24,021 --> 00:50:28,048
她是純粹的邪惡化身
Sir，what she is pure evil. 

792
00:50:28,191 --> 00:50:30,591
比野獸更令人害怕
More to be feared than a wild beast. 

793
00:50:30,727 --> 00:50:34,561
又餓又有尖牙的野獸
Hungry wild beast with gnashing teeth. 

794
00:50:34,698 --> 00:50:36,723
報復的，來自地獄的飢餓野獸...
Vengeful，hungry from hell beast...

795
00:50:36,867 --> 00:50:37,948
父親？
Father？

796
00:50:37,950 --> 00:50:39,028
但是很可愛！
Sweetness！

797
00:50:40,971 --> 00:50:42,529
不必傷害他的，父親
No need to hurt him，Father. 

798
00:50:42,672 --> 00:50:45,903
他會幫助我們，對吧，傑克？
He will help us. Won't you，Jack？

799
00:50:46,043 --> 00:50:47,909
瞧？到現在
You see？Even now，

800
00:50:47,911 --> 00:50:49,774
她還是關心你的安危
she attends to your welfare，

801
00:50:49,913 --> 00:50:53,474
雖然你一再說她是騙子
giving lie to the claims you make of her. 

802
00:51:01,058 --> 00:51:05,552
你會帶我們到青春之泉，對吧？
You will lead us to the Fountain. Yes？

803
00:51:06,363 --> 00:51:08,058
換另一個方式說吧
Put another way. 

804
00:51:08,865 --> 00:51:12,266
要是我來不及趕到青春之泉...
If I do not make it to the Fountain in time...

805
00:51:13,904 --> 00:51:16,896
...你也去不了
...neither will you. 

806
00:51:19,042 --> 00:51:21,107
我馬上仔細看
I'll have a wee look-see at those 

807
00:51:21,108 --> 00:51:23,172
這些航海圖，好吧？
charts straight away then，shall I？

808
00:51:26,917 --> 00:51:28,179
長官
Sir. 

809
00:51:31,054 --> 00:51:32,237
什麼事？
Aye？

810
00:51:32,239 --> 00:51:33,420
船長，長官
Captain，sir，

811
00:51:33,557 --> 00:51:35,957
長官，我在船員中聽到
I am unhappy to report rumors，sir，

812
00:51:36,093 --> 00:51:39,000
關於目的地不好的謠言
among the crew，as to our destination. 

813
00:51:39,463 --> 00:51:41,454
閉上你的嘴給我離開
Shut your trap and make way. 

814
00:51:45,469 --> 00:51:47,284
你想抗命
That's the way of it，then. 

815
00:51:47,286 --> 00:51:49,098
無意冒犯，長官
No disrespect，sir. 

816
00:51:49,906 --> 00:51:51,795
他們怕什麼？說出來
What do the men fear？Say it. 

817
00:51:51,797 --> 00:51:52,739
說出那個字
Speak the words. 

818
00:51:53,477 --> 00:51:54,808
白帽灣
Whitecap Bay. 

819
00:51:54,945 --> 00:51:58,073
是啊，白帽灣
Aye，Whitecap Bay. 

820
00:51:58,181 --> 00:52:00,229
所有沒用的水手
And every worthless seaman fears the name，

821
00:52:00,230 --> 00:52:02,277
都恐懼這名字
and rightly so，

822
00:52:02,419 --> 00:52:04,915
雖然少數人知道原因或膽敢詢問
though few know why or dare to ask. 

823
00:52:04,921 --> 00:52:06,548
傳說是真的？
Be the stories true？

824
00:52:06,723 --> 00:52:08,620
吉卜，說，是什麼讓你們動搖了
Say what robs you of your staunch heart，Gibbs，

825
00:52:08,658 --> 00:52:11,821
否則永遠留在幻想的領域
or forever leave it to the wider fields of fancy. 

826
00:52:14,498 --> 00:52:16,125
人魚，船長
Mermaids，Captain. 

827
00:52:16,266 --> 00:52:18,029
是啊，人魚
Aye. Mermaids. 

828
00:52:18,168 --> 00:52:20,319
大海食屍鬼，魔鬼魚
Sea ghouls，devil fish，

829
00:52:20,321 --> 00:52:22,470
令人恐懼的是超愛吃人肉
dreadful in hunger for flesh of man. 

830
00:52:22,472 --> 00:52:26,033
我們就是要經過人魚海域
Mermaid waters，that be our path. 

831
00:52:26,176 --> 00:52:27,768
顧好你的靈魂，吉卜
Cling to your soul，Gibbs，

832
00:52:27,878 --> 00:52:31,541
聽說人魚會把人吃到...
as mermaids be given to take the rest...

833
00:52:31,681 --> 00:52:33,114
...只剩骨頭
...to the bone. 

834
00:52:34,651 --> 00:52:36,233
冷靜！冷靜，大夥們！
Steady！Steady，men！

835
00:52:36,234 --> 00:52:37,814
鼓起你們的勇氣
Find your courage，

836
00:52:37,954 --> 00:52:39,854
不然就準備恐懼吧！
or be ready to purpose your fear！

837
00:52:39,990 --> 00:52:42,390
自求多福吧！
Save yourselves！

838
00:52:44,961 --> 00:52:46,395
有人落水！
Man overboard！

839
00:52:46,397 --> 00:52:47,828
不是！那是棄船者
Nay！A deserter. 

840
00:52:47,964 --> 00:52:48,846
改變航向
Come about. 

841
00:52:48,848 --> 00:52:49,727
不
Nay！

842
00:52:51,001 --> 00:52:52,335
各位
Gentlemen，

843
00:52:52,337 --> 00:52:54,154
我不會要求你們
I shall not ask any more of  

844
00:52:54,156 --> 00:52:55,971
做辦不到的事
any man than what that man can deliver，

845
00:52:55,973 --> 00:52:59,465
但我想問：我們是不是英國的臣民？
but I do ask this：Are we not king's men？

846
00:52:59,576 --> 00:53:01,043
是
Aye. 

847
00:53:01,178 --> 00:53:02,560
那我們是不是國王的好臣民？
On the king's mission？

848
00:53:02,562 --> 00:53:03,942
是
Aye. 

849
00:53:04,114 --> 00:53:06,230
當西班牙佬從旁經過時
I did not note any fear in the eyes 

850
00:53:06,232 --> 00:53:08,346
我在西班牙佬眼中看不到恐懼
of the Spanish as they passed us by. 

851
00:53:08,485 --> 00:53:09,950
你們敢不敢去白帽灣？
Are we not king's men？

852
00:53:09,952 --> 00:53:11,215
敢！
Aye！

853
00:53:11,354 --> 00:53:14,289
現在給我滾回自己的崗位幹活！
Aye！Hands all off，and bear away！

854
00:53:14,457 --> 00:53:17,392
直直航向白帽灣！
Stave on ahead to Whitecap Bay！

855
00:53:19,029 --> 00:53:21,395
航向，白帽灣！
Bear on，Whitecap Bay！

856
00:53:35,378 --> 00:53:36,868
來嘛
Come. 

857
00:53:37,013 --> 00:53:38,310
喝點酒？
Little drink？

858
00:53:38,481 --> 00:53:41,712
美酒，音樂，燭光
Wine，music，candlelight. 

859
00:53:41,851 --> 00:53:44,081
這種事我們早就做過，傑克
I think we've traveled down this road before，Jack. 

860
00:53:44,221 --> 00:53:46,052
沒錯，我們是做過
Yes，we have. 

861
00:53:47,023 --> 00:53:48,422
我記得很清楚
I remember it well. 

862
00:53:50,260 --> 00:53:55,095
纏繞，扭曲和轉動，迴轉，扭動著
Winding，twisting andturning，gyrating，writhing. 

863
00:53:55,232 --> 00:53:57,564
不停地扭動著
Incessant writhing. 

864
00:53:57,701 --> 00:53:59,566
記得聖多明哥嗎？
Do you recall Saint Dominique？

865
00:54:01,004 --> 00:54:02,562
拉馬提尼克島
La Martinique. 

866
00:54:02,706 --> 00:54:04,401
在聖多明哥我就想殺你了
I tried to kill you in Saint Dominique. 

867
00:54:04,541 --> 00:54:06,304
無所謂啦
Either or. 

868
00:54:07,110 --> 00:54:09,135
對一位大副幾乎沒有恰當的
Hardly appropriate for a first mate. 

869
00:54:09,279 --> 00:54:12,737
我是妳的第一次嗎？我總想知道
Was I the first？I've often wondered. 

870
00:54:12,882 --> 00:54:17,114
當你有慾望時真迷人，傑克
You can be so charming when you want something，Jack. 

871
00:54:17,254 --> 00:54:19,745
竅門是找出你想要什麼
The trick is finding out what. 

872
00:54:20,857 --> 00:54:22,950
事實，是什麼？
The truth，then，is it？

873
00:54:23,660 --> 00:54:26,151
黑鬍子已經達到他的目的
Blackbeard has served his purpose. 

874
00:54:26,296 --> 00:54:28,628
妳和我一起去青春之泉
You and I can go to the Fountain together，

875
00:54:28,765 --> 00:54:31,825
一起沐浴在青春之泉
where we shall bathe one another in equal shares of fame

876
00:54:31,968 --> 00:54:33,993
盡情享受各種歡愉
and other assorted debaucheries. 

877
00:54:34,137 --> 00:54:37,129
而我告訴你青春之泉的儀式
And I'll tell youthe ritual of the Fountain. 

878
00:54:37,274 --> 00:54:40,107
對，異教的儀式
Yes. The profane ritual. 

879
00:54:42,812 --> 00:54:45,007
我能信任你嗎，傑克？
Can I trust you，Jack？

880
00:54:45,148 --> 00:54:47,367
我需要你站在我這邊
I need you on my side. 

881
00:54:47,369 --> 00:54:49,585
最親愛的安潔莉卡
Oh，my dearest Angelica. 

882
00:54:49,686 --> 00:54:53,144
我們是神偷俠侶
You and I are asthick as thieves，love. 

883
00:54:53,290 --> 00:54:55,520
告訴我那個儀式
Tell me the rules. 

884
00:54:57,661 --> 00:55:01,324
青春之泉的泉水
Water from the Fountain of Youth. 

885
00:55:03,166 --> 00:55:06,602
人魚閃亮的淚水
The shimmering tear of a mermaid. 

886
00:55:06,703 --> 00:55:10,036
龐塞德萊昂的銀杯
The silver chalices of Ponce de Leon. 

887
00:55:11,975 --> 00:55:13,704
只要用這些東西...
With these items...

888
00:55:13,843 --> 00:55:14,907
怎樣？
Yes？

889
00:55:14,909 --> 00:55:15,970
用這些東西
With these items，

890
00:55:16,112 --> 00:55:19,513
你就能得到另一個人的全部歲月
you may take all the years of life from another，Jack. 

891
00:55:21,785 --> 00:55:23,616
傑克，你知道這意味著什麼
You know what that means. 

892
00:55:23,720 --> 00:55:26,655
我們倆不能單獨去
We cannot go alone，you and I. 

893
00:55:26,790 --> 00:55:29,054
儀式需要一名犧牲者
The ritual requires a victim. 

894
00:55:30,794 --> 00:55:32,728
這真不幸
That is unfortunate. 

895
00:55:32,730 --> 00:55:34,662
是啊
Yes，it is. 

896
00:55:35,665 --> 00:55:38,532
我對青春之泉的慾望都沒了
I find my desire for the Fountaing reatly lessened. 

897
00:55:39,936 --> 00:55:42,564
不過船上有你想要的東西
But there is something on board you do want. 

898
00:55:48,345 --> 00:55:49,710
黑鬍子來了怎麼辦？
What about Blackbeard？

899
00:55:49,846 --> 00:55:51,644
他在海圖室
He's in the chart room. 

900
00:55:51,646 --> 00:55:53,441
我們要快點
We'll have to be quick. 

901
00:56:02,525 --> 00:56:05,119
他把每艘船當成戰利品保存著
He keeps each ship as a prize. 

902
00:56:06,896 --> 00:56:09,126
只要你幫我
You help me，

903
00:56:09,128 --> 00:56:11,356
我保證讓你挑你要的船
and I promise you your pick. 

904
00:56:11,501 --> 00:56:14,902
雖然我知道你會挑哪一艘
Though I think I know the one you will choose. 

905
00:56:20,777 --> 00:56:23,268
鬼盜船在瓶子裡？
The Black Pearl in a bottle？

906
00:56:23,413 --> 00:56:25,142
鬼盜船怎麼會在瓶子裡？
Why is the Black Pearl in a bottle？

907
00:56:30,920 --> 00:56:33,787
那隻猴子縮小了還是那麼討厭
He's even more annoying in miniature. 

908
00:56:33,923 --> 00:56:35,937
我們就這麼說定了咯，傑克？
Do we have a deal，Jack？

909
00:56:35,939 --> 00:56:37,950
安潔莉卡，我瞭解妳
Angelica，I know you. 

910
00:56:38,094 --> 00:56:40,961
妳不會偷走無辜者的生命
You are not going to steal the life of some innocent man. 

911
00:56:41,531 --> 00:56:43,829
獨腿者的怎麼樣？
What about the one-legged man？

912
00:56:46,069 --> 00:56:47,730
傑克，我需要歲月
I need years，Jack. 

913
00:56:49,539 --> 00:56:51,257
不是為我
Not for me. 

914
00:56:51,259 --> 00:56:52,975
是為了我的父親
For my father. 

915
00:56:55,578 --> 00:56:57,910
我真的是黑鬍子的女兒
I am truly the daughter of Blackbeard. 

916
00:56:58,915 --> 00:57:01,110
妳迷失在自己的假話了
You've fallen for your own con，love. 

917
00:57:01,251 --> 00:57:03,515
不是的，他是我的父親
No，he is my father. 

918
00:57:03,686 --> 00:57:05,381
我對你說的假話不全是假的
The lies I told you were not lies. 

919
00:57:07,157 --> 00:57:10,058
妳對我說的假話都是真的？
You lied to me by telling me the truth？

920
00:57:10,160 --> 00:57:11,173
對
Yes. 

921
00:57:11,175 --> 00:57:12,185
這招厲害
That's very good. 

922
00:57:12,362 --> 00:57:13,579
我能用這招嗎？
May I use that？

923
00:57:13,581 --> 00:57:14,796
少來，我肯定你會的
I'm sure you will，anyway. 

924
00:57:14,931 --> 00:57:17,297
我當然會囉
Of course I will. 

925
00:57:17,434 --> 00:57:20,130
所以，妳不會放棄這個搜尋？
So，will you not give up this quest？

926
00:57:20,737 --> 00:57:22,301
我想要父愛，傑克
I want a father，Jack. 

927
00:57:22,303 --> 00:57:23,865
我不曾有過
I haven't had one. 

928
00:57:25,108 --> 00:57:28,407
安潔莉卡，妳的父親，黑鬍子...
Angelica，your father，Blackbeard...

929
00:57:29,946 --> 00:57:31,311
...他很邪惡
...he is evil，

930
00:57:31,448 --> 00:57:33,643
而且有機會他會殺了妳
and he will kill you given the chance. 

931
00:57:33,783 --> 00:57:35,330
他是無法被救贖的
He cannot be saved. 

932
00:57:35,332 --> 00:57:39,214
你又憑什麼來規定救贖界限？
And who are you to set the limits on redemption？

933
00:57:39,389 --> 00:57:41,839
你偷走了我的青春
You stole years of my life，Jack. 

934
00:57:41,841 --> 00:57:42,688
這是你欠我的
You owe me. 

935
00:57:42,826 --> 00:57:45,886
妳這是在自己找死
And you are en route to getting yourself killed，

936
00:57:46,062 --> 00:57:48,360
我不想袖手旁觀
and I am not inclined to stand by and watch. 

937
00:57:48,498 --> 00:57:52,229
白帽灣到了！
Whitecap Bay！

938
00:57:57,340 --> 00:57:59,086
全員集合！
All hands on deck！

939
00:57:59,088 --> 00:58:00,832
準備上長艇！
Set to the longboats！

940
00:58:04,814 --> 00:58:05,838
把漁網擺平！
Lay 'em out flat！

941
00:58:06,516 --> 00:58:07,617
不要打結
No tangles. 

942
00:58:07,619 --> 00:58:11,317
弄漂亮點迎接我們美麗的嬌客
Make 'em look pretty for our dainty guests. 

943
00:58:11,454 --> 00:58:13,354
我們需要燈光
We're gonna need light. 

944
00:58:13,356 --> 00:58:15,254
很強的燈光
A lot of light. 

945
00:58:17,026 --> 00:58:18,050
跟我來！
Come！

946
00:58:39,849 --> 00:58:42,460
聞到了嗎？鯨魚油，
Smell that？Whale oil. 

947
00:58:42,462 --> 00:58:45,082
燃燒的火光像是上帝的奇蹟
Stuff burns like a miracle from God. 

948
00:58:45,221 --> 00:58:47,087
你能點燃燈塔嗎？
Can you make it work？

949
00:58:47,089 --> 00:58:48,952
英國佬製造的
Made by the English. 

950
00:58:49,125 --> 00:58:50,217
我們就不要期望太大了
Let's not get our hopes up. 

951
00:59:01,237 --> 00:59:03,337
月亮新的週期
The old moon in the arms of the new one. 

952
00:59:03,339 --> 00:59:05,473
夏季第一次開始時
First of the summer. 

