01:15:06,284 --> 01:15:08,775
父親，不能相信他，我去
We cannot trust him，Father. I'll go. 

1130
01:15:09,621 --> 01:15:11,350
她自願去
She'll go. 

1131
01:15:15,360 --> 01:15:16,725
青春之泉還有多遠？
How much farther to the Fountain？

1132
01:15:16,862 --> 01:15:18,557
我快沒有時間了
I'm running out of time. 

1133
01:15:20,532 --> 01:15:22,693
沿著這條河，向北走一天
About a day's march north，following that river，

1134
01:15:22,834 --> 01:15:24,580
會到達一連串的池塘
you'll get to a series of pools. 

1135
01:15:24,581 --> 01:15:26,326
就很接近了
Then you're close. 

1136
01:15:28,807 --> 01:15:30,069
你要跳下去
You will go. 

1137
01:15:32,978 --> 01:15:35,276
我就知道會這樣
I was sure it would come to this. 

1138
01:15:48,860 --> 01:15:50,942
都說人從上面
You know that feeling you get sometimes 

1139
01:15:50,943 --> 01:15:53,024
往下看的時候？
when you're standing in a high place？

1140
01:15:53,164 --> 01:15:55,098
會有跳下去的衝動？
Sudden urge to jump？

1141
01:15:57,002 --> 01:15:58,560
但我沒有
I don't have it. 

1142
01:15:59,938 --> 01:16:01,496
我需要那兩隻聖盃
I need those chalices. 

1143
01:16:01,606 --> 01:16:02,852
斃了我吧
Shoot. 

1144
01:16:02,853 --> 01:16:04,097
我不想摔死
Save me the bother of the fall. 

1145
01:16:04,242 --> 01:16:07,302
你要跳下去，然後回來...
You will go. You will return...

1146
01:16:08,613 --> 01:16:10,604
...不然我就殺了她
...or I will kill her. 

1147
01:16:13,418 --> 01:16:14,942
你不會殺死自己的女兒
You won't kill your own daughter. 

1148
01:16:15,086 --> 01:16:17,884
舵手，給我六把手槍
Quartermaster，get me six more pistols，

1149
01:16:18,023 --> 01:16:19,615
兩把裝上子彈
remove the shot from all but two，

1150
01:16:19,758 --> 01:16:22,249
但別告訴我是那兩把
but do not tell me which two. 

1151
01:16:24,529 --> 01:16:27,123
史派洛先生，你來選
You get to choose，Mr. Sparrow. 

1152
01:16:29,901 --> 01:16:31,095
不
No. 

1153
01:16:33,305 --> 01:16:34,329
不
No. 

1154
01:16:37,442 --> 01:16:38,859
就這把
Yes. 

1155
01:16:38,861 --> 01:16:40,275
你確定？
You're sure？

1156
01:16:40,412 --> 01:16:41,879
當然了
'Course I am. 

1157
01:16:50,088 --> 01:16:51,146
再挑一把
Again. 

1158
01:16:52,657 --> 01:16:55,217
拜託，根本沒裝子彈
Please，they're not even loaded. 

1159
01:17:00,131 --> 01:17:01,428
再挑一把
Again. 

1160
01:17:02,267 --> 01:17:04,167
你這麼想殺她
If you're so keen on killing her，

1161
01:17:04,302 --> 01:17:05,502
為什麼不讓她跳？
why don't you just let her jump？

1162
01:17:05,504 --> 01:17:06,702
什麼？
What？

1163
01:17:07,472 --> 01:17:09,963
如果你摔死
If you jump and die，

1164
01:17:10,108 --> 01:17:13,771
那就輪到她
then she will have her chance. 

1165
01:17:13,912 --> 01:17:15,379
再挑一把
Again. 

1166
01:17:18,617 --> 01:17:20,517
喂...
Oi...

1167
01:17:20,652 --> 01:17:22,586
...從上面跳下去
...if I jump，

1168
01:17:22,587 --> 01:17:24,520
我能活命嗎？
will I survive？

1169
01:17:26,825 --> 01:17:28,190
娃娃
The doll. 

1170
01:17:44,509 --> 01:17:46,893
現在你能活命了
Yes，now you will survive. 

1171
01:17:46,895 --> 01:17:49,276
胡說八道！我來跳
This is nonsense！I'm going！

1172
01:18:07,999 --> 01:18:11,230
濕了，我又濕了！
Wet. Wet again. 

1173
01:18:13,538 --> 01:18:14,989
我們繼續
We go on. 

1174
01:18:14,991 --> 01:18:16,439
往北走向青春之泉
Due north to the Fountain. 

1175
01:18:17,275 --> 01:18:18,640
父親，幹得好
Well played，Father. 

1176
01:18:20,378 --> 01:18:22,710
你早知道哪把槍有子彈，對吧？
You knew which guns were loaded，right？

1177
01:18:25,417 --> 01:18:27,408
乖女兒，當然了
Of course，my love. 

1178
01:18:37,062 --> 01:18:39,792
要是有地圖就好了
Be nice to have a map about now. 

1179
01:18:39,964 --> 01:18:41,591
或是一艘船
Or a ship. 

1180
01:18:42,333 --> 01:18:46,064
站住！千萬別動
Stop！Hold very still. 

1181
01:18:47,505 --> 01:18:51,032
別讓牠碰到你的皮膚
Ye dare not let it touch your skin. 

1182
01:18:59,751 --> 01:19:03,016
怎麼？有個嗜好有什麼不對？
What？What be wrong with an older man having a hobby？

1183
01:19:03,121 --> 01:19:05,681
你停下來幹嘛，嗯？快走！
What are you stopping for，eh？Push on！

1184
01:19:05,790 --> 01:19:06,905
快走！
Push on！

1185
01:19:06,907 --> 01:19:08,124
等你們死了有的是時間睡
You can sleep when you're dead. 

1186
01:19:08,126 --> 01:19:09,354
快走！
Push on！

1187
01:19:10,929 --> 01:19:14,296
青春之泉眷顧我們
Fortune continues to favor us. 

1188
01:19:42,060 --> 01:19:44,290
聖地牙哥號
The Santiago. 

1189
01:19:44,429 --> 01:19:47,159
著名的龐塞德萊昂指揮艦
Famously captained by Ponce de Leon. 

1190
01:19:49,934 --> 01:19:51,401
那裡沒有人
There's no one there. 

1191
01:19:51,503 --> 01:19:52,527
對的
Right，then. 

1192
01:20:27,205 --> 01:20:28,638
我們不能停下來
We must not stop. 

1193
01:20:36,648 --> 01:20:38,445
妳得走路
You will walk. 

1194
01:20:57,569 --> 01:20:59,730
我不會走路
I cannot. 

1195
01:20:59,871 --> 01:21:01,668
不走就死
Walk or die. 

1196
01:21:08,112 --> 01:21:09,340
我來扶妳
Put your arms around me. 

1197
01:21:09,480 --> 01:21:11,181
我沒要求幫助
I do not ask for help. 

1198
01:21:11,183 --> 01:21:12,881
但妳需要幫助
But you need it. 

1199
01:21:29,801 --> 01:21:31,951
我們在趕時間，對吧？
We're in a hurry，yes？

1200
01:21:31,953 --> 01:21:34,101
不要落後了
Do not fall behind. 

1201
01:21:53,424 --> 01:21:55,187
在這暫停一下！
Hold here 'til I say！

1202
01:22:08,239 --> 01:22:10,104
妳真美麗
Such beauty. 

1203
01:22:10,241 --> 01:22:13,574
妳一定是上帝親手製作的
Surely you're one of God's own creations，

1204
01:22:13,711 --> 01:22:16,646
並不是沒上方舟的
and not a descendant of those dark creatures

1205
01:22:16,781 --> 01:22:19,079
那些落難者的後代
who found no refuge on the Ark. 

1206
01:22:21,853 --> 01:22:23,980
妳真美麗...
Such beauty...

1207
01:22:25,256 --> 01:22:26,883
...但是致命
...and yet deadly. 

1208
01:22:27,859 --> 01:22:29,588
致命？不是的
Deadly？No. 

1209
01:22:29,590 --> 01:22:31,317
妳攻擊我
You attacked me. 

1210
01:22:31,462 --> 01:22:34,442
不是這樣的
No. 

1211
01:22:34,443 --> 01:22:36,422
你和他們不一樣
You are different. 

1212
01:22:37,335 --> 01:22:38,563
不一樣？
Different？

1213
01:22:38,670 --> 01:22:40,684
不是嗎？
Are you not？

1214
01:22:40,685 --> 01:22:42,697
你保護了我
You protect. 

1215
01:22:46,110 --> 01:22:47,168
是妳做的？
Did you？

1216
01:22:48,813 --> 01:22:51,611
是妳把我從爆炸中救出來
You pushed me down out of the way. 

1217
01:22:52,750 --> 01:22:54,997
你看到青春之泉嗎？
You see the Fountain？

1218
01:22:54,999 --> 01:22:57,244
沒有，但是我們很接近了
No，but we are close. 

1219
01:22:57,789 --> 01:22:58,722
把那怪物帶來
Bring the creature. 

1220
01:22:58,723 --> 01:22:59,654
罩住牠的頭
Cover its head. 

1221
01:22:59,791 --> 01:23:01,782
她有名字！
She has a name！

1222
01:23:06,297 --> 01:23:07,821
請賜教
Pray tell. 

1223
01:23:14,038 --> 01:23:15,938
她是莎琳娜
She is Syrena. 

1224
01:23:56,881 --> 01:23:58,405
龐塞德萊昂
Ponce de Leon. 

1225
01:24:02,086 --> 01:24:05,783
40個海盜做上40個晚上發財夢
If 40 pirates dreamt 40 nights of treasure，

1226
01:24:05,957 --> 01:24:09,518
也夢不到這麼多的金銀財寶
it would not match the contents of this room. 

1227
01:24:09,660 --> 01:24:11,218
你
You. 

1228
01:24:13,998 --> 01:24:14,897
你
You. 

1229
01:24:14,899 --> 01:24:15,795
不...
No...

1230
01:24:16,968 --> 01:24:18,100
...你
...you. 

1231
01:24:18,102 --> 01:24:19,232
我先來的
I was here first. 

1232
01:24:19,370 --> 01:24:21,384
你，為什麼會在這裡？
You，why are you here？

1233
01:24:21,386 --> 01:24:23,397
黑鬍子派我來的
Blackbeard sent me. 

1234
01:24:23,541 --> 01:24:24,787
你又是為什麼咧？
Why are you？

1235
01:24:24,789 --> 01:24:26,032
銀杯
Silver chalices

1236
01:24:26,177 --> 01:24:27,861
替我的國王取回
for my royal liege. 

1237
01:24:27,863 --> 01:24:29,544
噢，拜託
Oh，please. 

1238
01:24:30,782 --> 01:24:32,579
退後，退後！我們得保持平衡！
Back，back！We have to balance it out！

1239
01:24:34,552 --> 01:24:37,146
整艘船會滑下去！
The whole ship will slide！

1240
01:24:40,925 --> 01:24:42,552
對喔
Right，then. 

1241
01:24:42,693 --> 01:24:45,663
如果我們各挑一個
What if we each choose an item 

1242
01:24:45,664 --> 01:24:48,632
差不多重的東西？
of approximately equal weight？

1243
01:24:51,269 --> 01:24:52,736
放回去！
Put it back！

1244
01:24:54,238 --> 01:24:56,297
我們什麼都別碰！
We touch nothing！

1245
01:25:04,215 --> 01:25:05,182
那個呢？
What about that？

1246
01:25:05,349 --> 01:25:07,715
聖盃
The chalices. 

1247
01:25:09,420 --> 01:25:10,944
喂！你憑什麼可以先看？
Oi！Why do you get to look first？

1248
01:25:11,089 --> 01:25:12,784
好吧
Fine，then. 

1249
01:25:32,043 --> 01:25:32,822
我們一起看
Together. 

1250
01:25:32,824 --> 01:25:33,601
我們一起看
Together. 

1251
01:25:36,314 --> 01:25:37,338
是石頭
Rocks. 

1252
01:25:38,416 --> 01:25:39,781
西班牙佬
The Spanish. 

1253
01:25:40,485 --> 01:25:42,180
他們趕在我們前面
They're ahead of us，mate. 

1254
01:25:43,087 --> 01:25:44,720
我要看看那張地圖
I shall have a look at that map. 

1255
01:25:44,722 --> 01:25:46,352
一定有鬼...
If it's what I fear...

1256
01:25:56,434 --> 01:25:58,664
不然他們幹嘛把地圖留下來
I wonder why they left this behind. 

1257
01:26:01,639 --> 01:26:05,439
別動那張地圖
Don't touch the map. 

1258
01:26:10,781 --> 01:26:11,873
他們知道路線
They know the path，

1259
01:26:12,016 --> 01:26:13,967
但我知道
but I can also see where 

1260
01:26:13,968 --> 01:26:15,918
他們會在哪兒紮營
they'll most likely make camp. 

1261
01:26:29,367 --> 01:26:30,698
傑克！
Jack！

1262
01:26:33,871 --> 01:26:38,035
吉卜，我正準備策劃去監獄救你
Gibbs，I was just on me way to break you out of jail. 

1263
01:26:39,977 --> 01:26:41,501
你偷走了我的地圖
You stole my map. 

1264
01:26:42,046 --> 01:26:44,514
夠了，該走了
Right. Best be started. 

1265
01:26:47,552 --> 01:26:49,076
遵命？
Ol？

1266
01:27:06,470 --> 01:27:07,960
人魚
Mermaids. 

1267
01:27:10,808 --> 01:27:13,743
注意，這些池塘很深
Careful，these pools run deep. 

1268
01:27:13,878 --> 01:27:16,251
要是她逃走，一切就完了
If she escapes，all is lost. 

1269
01:27:16,252 --> 01:27:17,439
舵手
Quartermaster. 

1270
01:27:19,083 --> 01:27:22,382
看，快看！
Look. Look！

1271
01:27:23,955 --> 01:27:25,440
她被釘住
Staked out to die，

1272
01:27:25,441 --> 01:27:26,924
被太陽曬死
to dry in the sun. 

1273
01:27:27,058 --> 01:27:28,856
身體只有一半在水裡
Only half in the water. 

1274
01:27:28,858 --> 01:27:30,653
雖然活不了
Not enough to live，

1275
01:27:30,828 --> 01:27:34,992
但是卻能讓她慢慢折磨而死
but just enough to make the dying slow. 

1276
01:27:36,200 --> 01:27:37,224
想想看
Think on it. 

1277
01:27:37,368 --> 01:27:39,069
妳的族人，被殺死
Your people，murdered，

1278
01:27:39,070 --> 01:27:40,769
她們的淚水被收集
harvested for their tears. 

1279
01:27:40,905 --> 01:27:45,239
莎琳娜，妳怎麼不哭？
Syrena，won't you cry？

1280
01:27:46,110 --> 01:27:47,941
你們全都快死了，你也是
All die，even you. 

1281
01:27:48,079 --> 01:27:49,808
我聽得見，很快
Soon，I hear. 

1282
01:27:49,810 --> 01:27:51,537
聽好...
Listen...

1283
01:27:53,584 --> 01:27:55,449
聽好
Listen. 

1284
01:27:55,586 --> 01:27:58,919
聽得見妳的姊妹們在尖叫嗎？
Can you not hear your sisters scream？

1285
01:27:59,056 --> 01:28:01,490
妳聽不見是嗎？
Do you not hear them？

1286
01:28:02,526 --> 01:28:05,324
我們只需要一滴淚水
We need but one tear. 

1287
01:28:08,199 --> 01:28:09,496
低等的生物！
Vile creature！

1288
01:28:09,634 --> 01:28:10,932
切斷她的手指，一根一根！
Chop off her fingers，one by one！

1289
01:28:10,933 --> 01:28:12,228
窒息她！
Choke her！

1290
01:28:12,336 --> 01:28:14,964
挖出她的眼睛採集淚水！
Cut out the tears from behind the eyes！

1291
01:28:15,106 --> 01:28:16,437
妳怎麼不說話？
Where's your voice in this？

1292
01:28:17,308 --> 01:28:18,821
日出後
Maybe she'll have a change of heart 

1293
01:28:18,822 --> 01:28:20,334
她也許會改變主意
when the sun rises. 

1294
01:28:20,478 --> 01:28:22,429
對，她會被曬死
Oh，aye，she will burn，

1295
01:28:22,431 --> 01:28:24,380
但我等不及了
but I cannot wait for the sun. 

1296
01:28:24,548 --> 01:28:26,243
也許我們該升火
Perhaps we should build a fire. 

1297
01:28:26,350 --> 01:28:27,431
不
No. 

1298
01:28:27,433 --> 01:28:28,511
牧師，別想違抗我
Do not contest me，cleric. 

1299
01:28:28,653 --> 01:28:30,183
你不能折磨她
You will not torture her. 

1300
01:28:30,185 --> 01:28:31,713
我們只需要一滴淚水
We need only one tear. 

1301
01:28:31,889 --> 01:28:35,017
我會把她身上的鱗片刮下來
I will tear every scale from her body one by one if I see fit. 

1302
01:28:35,159 --> 01:28:36,717
如果你不高興，就滾回去禱告吧
If that displeases you，go pray. 

1303
01:28:36,894 --> 01:28:37,925
我錯了
I was wrong. 

1304
01:28:37,926 --> 01:28:38,958
不是每個靈魂都能救贖
Not every soul can be saved. 

1305
01:28:38,959 --> 01:28:39,988
你的就不能
Yours cannot. 

1306
01:28:40,131 --> 01:28:41,565
看哪，各位
Behold，gentlemen，

1307
01:28:41,566 --> 01:28:42,998
信仰就是這麼不可靠
a man formerly of faith. 

1308
01:28:43,134 --> 01:28:44,585
你口中的低等生物
That vile creature，as you call her，

1309
01:28:44,586 --> 01:28:46,035
遠勝你百倍
is worth a hundred of you. 

1310
01:28:46,170 --> 01:28:47,933
喔，你關心她？
Oh，you care for her？

1311
01:28:49,940 --> 01:28:51,965
你喜歡她
You fancy her. 

1312
01:28:53,644 --> 01:28:56,374
別否認，我全都看在眼裡
And do not deny what is clear to my eyes. 

1313
01:28:58,182 --> 01:28:59,308
問題是...
Question is...

1314
01:29:02,486 --> 01:29:04,477
...她喜不喜歡你？
...does she fancy you？

1315
01:29:06,724 --> 01:29:08,922
天啊，她喜歡你
By God，she does. 

1316
01:29:08,923 --> 01:29:10,319
咱們走運了
We are in luck！

1317
01:29:11,729 --> 01:29:13,629
流一滴淚水...
Bring forth a tear...

1318
01:29:15,132 --> 01:29:17,657
...或是親眼看著他死
...or witness the death of this poor soul. 

1319
01:29:19,804 --> 01:29:23,240
莎琳娜，要是妳能擠出一滴淚
Syrena，if you could manage a tear，

1320
01:29:23,374 --> 01:29:24,966
我就感激不盡
I would be grateful. 

1321
01:29:26,310 --> 01:29:27,902
她可憐你
Sadness，yes，

1322
01:29:28,045 --> 01:29:30,747
但並不悲傷...還沒有
but no sorrow... yet. 

1323
01:29:30,749 --> 01:29:33,449
父親！你不能殺他
Not by your hand，Father！

1324
01:29:33,617 --> 01:29:36,245
時間不會等待任何人，舵手
Time and tide wait for none.Quartermaster. 

1325
01:29:48,566 --> 01:29:52,058
好哇，人魚真的很頑固
Aye，mermaids are tough. 

1326
01:29:52,203 --> 01:29:54,228
這些怪物
The lot of them. 

1327
01:29:54,372 --> 01:29:56,574
把她跟其他人魚一樣綁起來
Tie her up like the others. 

1328
01:29:56,576 --> 01:29:58,775
把他的屍體丟掉
And get rid of this. 

1329
01:30:03,347 --> 01:30:04,843
妳有信心？
You are confident？

1330
01:30:04,845 --> 01:30:06,339
當然
Yes. 

1331
01:30:06,450 --> 01:30:09,442
我是女人，她也是
I am a woman. So is she. 

1332
01:30:17,461 --> 01:30:18,974
傑克，你玩什麼把戲？
What's your play，Jack？

1333
01:30:18,976 --> 01:30:20,487
居然和巴船長合作
Throwing in with Barbossa. 

1334
01:30:21,565 --> 01:30:23,362
有一個女生...
There is a girl...

1335
01:30:23,467 --> 01:30:25,083
...一個女人
...a female 

1336
01:30:25,084 --> 01:30:26,698
...我們的異性
...of the opposite sex. 

1337
01:30:26,804 --> 01:30:28,784
你幾時沒有過女人？
When is there not？

1338
01:30:28,786 --> 01:30:30,763
或許我應該說「小妞」
Perhaps I should say「damsel. 」

1339
01:30:30,908 --> 01:30:32,421
你要營救一個小妞？
You're rescuing a damsel？

1340
01:30:32,423 --> 01:30:33,934
好啊，這倒新鮮
Well，there's a first. 

1341
01:30:34,078 --> 01:30:37,309
對，不過就是很久以前
Yes，but it's just that I may have caused said damsel

1342
01:30:37,448 --> 01:30:39,246
我可能對這位小妞造成傷害了
some manner of harm many moons ago. 

1343
01:30:39,248 --> 01:30:41,043
說實話吧
Out with it. 

1344
01:30:41,152 --> 01:30:44,485
吉卜，這女人來自塞維利亞
Gibbs，this is the woman from Seville. 

1345
01:30:44,622 --> 01:30:47,099
啊，你假裝愛她
Ah，you pretended to love her，

1346
01:30:47,100 --> 01:30:48,690
然後傷了她的心
then you left her and broke her heart. 

1347
01:30:48,692 --> 01:30:49,691
更糟
Worse. 

1348
01:30:49,692 --> 01:30:53,391
我可能有過，一下下，怎麼說...
I may have had，briefly，mind you...

1349
01:30:55,566 --> 01:30:57,148
...心動
...stirrings. 

1350
01:30:57,150 --> 01:30:58,729
心動？
Stirrings？

1351
01:30:58,836 --> 01:31:00,333
心動
Stirrings. 

1352
01:31:00,335 --> 01:31:01,582
你說什麼？
What？

1353
01:31:01,583 --> 01:31:02,829
你是說，動真情了？
Like feelings，you mean？

1354
01:31:02,973 --> 01:31:03,430
不
No，no，no. 

1355
01:31:03,431 --> 01:31:04,486
不算是真情
Not quite all the way to feelings. 

1356
01:31:04,487 --> 01:31:05,999
更像是...
More like...

1357
01:31:10,114 --> 01:31:11,848
好啦，是真情，敗給你了
All right，feelings，damn you. 

1358
01:31:11,849 --> 01:31:14,199
但你還是拋棄了她
And you left her still. 

1359
01:31:14,200 --> 01:31:16,548
你真卑鄙
That's low. 

1360
01:31:17,988 --> 01:31:19,216
謝謝誇獎
Thank you. 

1361
01:31:26,130 --> 01:31:27,563
最好不要硬來
Stealth over force. 

1362
01:31:27,731 --> 01:31:31,462
考慮你的狀況，接下來讓我來吧
I'll take it from here on account of your condition. 

1363
01:31:32,603 --> 01:31:34,468
你的假腿沒被白蟻蛀掉吧？
You don't have termites，do you？

1364
01:31:34,605 --> 01:31:36,573
傑克，謝謝你的關心
I appreciate your concern，Jack，

1365
01:31:36,740 --> 01:31:39,231
但我還是要跟你一起去
but I'll be keeping you company all the same. 

1366
01:31:39,410 --> 01:31:40,940
少校，留在這裡
Hold here，Lieutenant Commander. 

1367
01:31:40,942 --> 01:31:42,470
等我的信號
Wait for my signal. 

1368
01:32:14,445 --> 01:32:15,492
在那裡，那一個
There. That one. 

1369
01:32:15,494 --> 01:32:16,538
他一定是首領
That be the leader. 

1370
01:32:16,680 --> 01:32:19,171
記住他的帳篷，因為那...
Make note of his tent because that's where...

1371
01:32:20,651 --> 01:32:22,767
不，等等
No，wait. 

1372
01:32:22,769 --> 01:32:24,883
老天，銀杯就在那裡
By God，that must be them right there. 

1373
01:32:28,392 --> 01:32:30,622
你的劍有股怪味
Your sword smells funny. 

1374
01:32:30,794 --> 01:32:35,697
那是毒蟾蜍的毒液
Aye. Poison from the innards of poisonous toads. 

1375
01:32:35,833 --> 01:32:37,380
只要被刮傷
Just a scratch，

1376
01:32:37,381 --> 01:32:38,927
馬上沒命
you're a dead man in minutes. 

1377
01:32:39,069 --> 01:32:41,401
你能不能把劍指向別的方向？
Would you mind pointing it the other way？

1378
01:32:41,539 --> 01:32:43,302
我不喜歡蟾蜍
I don't like toads. 

1379
01:32:48,178 --> 01:32:49,896
你在幹嘛？
What are you doing？

1380
01:32:49,898 --> 01:32:51,614
安排脫逃路線啊
Planning an escape route. 

1381
01:32:51,749 --> 01:32:53,797
你不都是這樣做的？
Isn't that how you do it？

1382
01:32:53,799 --> 01:32:55,845
是啊
Yes. 

1383
01:32:55,953 --> 01:32:57,517
但有時候我會...
Or sometimes I just...

1384
01:32:57,518 --> 01:32:59,081
隨機應變
improvise. 

1385
01:33:26,083 --> 01:33:27,573
現在要做什麼？
Now what？

1386
01:33:28,452 --> 01:33:30,977
我們慢慢走出去
We stroll out，slow and steady. 

1387
01:33:31,121 --> 01:33:32,952
別當自己是外人
Just like we belong. 

1388
01:34:32,383 --> 01:34:34,516
莎琳娜，對不起
I'm sorry，Syrena. 

1389
01:34:34,548 --> 01:34:36,649
菲利普，你還活著
Philip，you're alive. 

1390
01:34:36,787 --> 01:34:38,880
對
Yes. 

1391
01:34:38,882 --> 01:34:40,985
你回來救我
You came for me. 

1392
01:34:42,826 --> 01:34:44,350
為什麼？
Why？

1393
01:34:46,463 --> 01:34:48,761
妳很不同，不是嗎？
You're different，are you not？

1394
01:34:50,968 --> 01:34:55,337
妳不是很善良？有同情心？
Do you know not of kindness？Compassion？

1395
01:35:12,523 --> 01:35:14,514
為什麼人魚
Tears of sorrow，never. 

1396
01:35:14,658 --> 01:35:17,092
悲傷痛苦沒有淚水
Mermaids be too tough for that. 

1397
01:35:17,227 --> 01:35:19,388
快樂感動才會有...
But tears of joy...

1398
01:35:20,898 --> 01:35:23,332
聽說這種淚水更有效
They say these be the more potent anyway. 

1399
01:35:23,434 --> 01:35:24,930
莎琳娜，我發誓
Syrena，on my word，

1400
01:35:24,931 --> 01:35:26,426
這與我無關
I had no part in this. 

1401
01:35:27,705 --> 01:35:29,138
放了她，你不需要她了
Let her go. You don't need her now. 

1402
01:35:29,306 --> 01:35:32,241
放了她？不行
Let her go？No. 

1403
01:35:32,376 --> 01:35:33,872
把她綁緊
Secure her bonds. 

1404
01:35:33,874 --> 01:35:35,368
讓她自生自滅
We leave her with her own. 

1405
01:35:44,922 --> 01:35:46,913
你的逃跑路線呢？
How's that escape route working？

1406
01:35:47,057 --> 01:35:50,026
現在只能靠你隨機應變啦
Here's your chance to improvise. 

1407
01:35:50,127 --> 01:35:51,458
我也想呀
I'm attempting it. 

1408
01:35:51,595 --> 01:35:54,428
只要弄鬆一隻手就行
I might be able to get a hand loose. 

1409
01:35:54,565 --> 01:35:56,829
喔，你藏了刀子，太好了
Oh，you got a knife. That's very good. 

1410
01:35:57,935 --> 01:35:59,459
比那更好
Better. 

1411
01:36:04,908 --> 01:36:06,170
我也要一支
I want one of those. 

1412
01:36:10,881 --> 01:36:12,997
敬復仇
Here's to revenge. 

1413
01:36:12,998 --> 01:36:15,113
甜蜜的復仇
Sweet and clear. 

1414
01:36:15,252 --> 01:36:17,482
什麼復仇？
Revenge？

1415
01:36:17,484 --> 01:36:19,712
老巴，行了，別裝了
Come，come，Hector. 

1416
01:36:19,823 --> 01:36:21,256
如果你想要聖盃
If you wanted the chalices，

1417
01:36:21,391 --> 01:36:24,087
你就會看出它們不見了
you'd seen they were missing and gone. 

1418
01:36:24,228 --> 01:36:27,391
你趴在那，等著偷襲黑鬍子
You were lying in wait，for Blackbeard. 

1419
01:36:29,366 --> 01:36:32,597
喬治王，私掠船，假髮
King George. Privateer. Wig. 

1420
01:36:33,737 --> 01:36:35,170
全都是裝出來的
Cheap theatrical facade. 

1421
01:36:35,305 --> 01:36:36,739
我才不信
I'm not buying it. 

1422
01:36:36,741 --> 01:36:38,172
那天晚上你又不在場
You weren't there that night. 

1423
01:36:38,308 --> 01:36:40,225
失去鬼盜船的那晚
When the Pearl was lost？

1424
01:36:40,227 --> 01:36:42,142
是被搶走，不是失去
Taken，not lost. 

1425
01:36:44,748 --> 01:36:48,878
我們在伊斯帕尼奧拉海岸被突擊
We were off the coast of Hispaniola when we came under attack. 

1426
01:36:49,052 --> 01:36:52,488
完全沒有預警也沒得交涉
No provocation nor warning nor offer of parley. 

1427
01:36:52,623 --> 01:36:55,285
我們被炮火猛烈攻擊
We were peppered with cannon fire. 

1428
01:36:56,426 --> 01:36:59,657
然後在鬼盜船下的海水開始攪動
And then the sea beneath the Pearl began to roil. 

1429
01:37:01,198 --> 01:37:03,632
鬼盜船劇烈地搖晃
The Pearl was pitching and yawing violently. 

1430
01:37:03,767 --> 01:37:05,632
每個跳板，每個欄杆
Every plank，every rail，

1431
01:37:05,769 --> 01:37:08,636
每個帆柱，一下子，開始吱吱作響
every spar，all at once，began to creak. 

1432
01:37:08,772 --> 01:37:11,798
船上的纜繩就像有生命一樣
The rigging had come to life. 

1433
01:37:11,942 --> 01:37:14,638
我們自己的船居然跟我們做對...
Our own ship turned against us...

1434
01:37:14,778 --> 01:37:18,043
...綁著船員，像蛇一樣綁著他們
...tangling the crew，wrapping around 'em like snakes. 

1435
01:37:18,182 --> 01:37:20,582
還纏上了我的腿
And wrapping around me leg. 

1436
01:37:20,751 --> 01:37:23,151
但我雙手是自由的而且手裡還握著劍
But me arms were free and me sword was to hand. 

1437
01:37:23,287 --> 01:37:26,814
我的船由我主宰，不是黑鬍子
I am the master of me ship，not Blackbeard. 

1438
01:37:26,957 --> 01:37:30,449
我的生命由我主宰，不是黑鬍子
I am the master of my fate，not Blackbeard. 

1439
01:37:31,461 --> 01:37:33,827
所以我做了我該做的事
So I did what needed done. 

1440
01:37:40,671 --> 01:37:42,605
我活下來了
I survived. 

1441
01:37:44,174 --> 01:37:48,372
...你不是來找青春之泉的
So... you're not after the Fountain. 

1442
01:37:48,512 --> 01:37:52,175
我才不管喬治王或那些
I care not for King George or tavern yarns

1443
01:37:52,316 --> 01:37:54,546
可以治癒腿傷的無稽之說
that give hope for a healed limb. 

1444
01:37:56,186 --> 01:37:58,018
我甚至願意犧牲左手
But I'd give my left arm 

1445
01:37:58,019 --> 01:37:59,849
換取殺黑鬍子的機會
for a chance at Blackbeard. 

1446
01:38:00,057 --> 01:38:01,542
不是右手？
Not your right？

1447
01:38:01,544 --> 01:38:03,026
我需要好用的右手
I need me good arm

1448
01:38:03,160 --> 01:38:07,824
把毒劍刺進他的心臟
to drive my poisoned blade through his heart. 

1449
01:38:08,799 --> 01:38:11,233
老兄，你會有機會的
I'll see you get the chance，mate. 

1450
01:39:29,980 --> 01:39:31,311
俘虜逃走了
The prisoner's escaping. 

1451
01:39:38,588 --> 01:39:41,284
他逃走了！散開！找到他！
He's escaping！Fan out！Find him！

1452
01:39:41,425 --> 01:39:42,517
走！快走！
Go！Go！

1453
01:39:44,594 --> 01:39:47,461
別開槍！我要抓活的！
Hold your fire！I want him alive！

1454
01:39:55,672 --> 01:39:57,640
我覺得那就是信號了
I figured that was the signal. 

1455
01:40:40,717 --> 01:40:42,463
快走！準備出發！
Go！Prepare to move out！

1456
01:40:42,465 --> 01:40:44,209
敵人很快就會找到我們
The enemy is soon upon us. 

1457
01:40:45,956 --> 01:40:47,424
傑克，抱歉沒拿到聖盃
I'm sorry about the chalices，Jack，

1458
01:40:47,425 --> 01:40:48,891
但我在趕時間
but I've an appointment to keep. 

1459
01:40:49,026 --> 01:40:50,522
我不會回去拿的
I'll not be going back. 

1460
01:40:50,524 --> 01:40:52,018
沒必要
No need. 

1461
01:40:52,162 --> 01:40:53,675
要不要來一杯？
Shall we have a drink？

1462
01:40:53,677 --> 01:40:55,188
我們去青春之泉喝
We'll drink at the Fountain. 

1463
01:41:13,550 --> 01:41:15,331
為什麼每次見面
How is it we can never meet without  

1464
01:41:15,332 --> 01:41:17,111
你都拿著東西指著我？
you pointing something at me？

1465
01:41:18,321 --> 01:41:20,221
史派洛，你把聖盃帶來了？
You brought the chalices，Sparrow？

1466
01:41:20,357 --> 01:41:22,951
是的，喂！
Aye. Oi！

1467
01:41:26,430 --> 01:41:27,994
你還帶了個朋友
I see you brought a friend. 

1468
01:41:27,996 --> 01:41:29,558
是的
I did. 

1469
01:41:29,699 --> 01:41:32,930
獨腿者，在附近？
And the one-legged man，he is near. Aye？

1470
01:41:33,070 --> 01:41:34,469
是的
Aye. 

1471
01:41:35,272 --> 01:41:36,296
好了...
Now...

1472
01:41:36,440 --> 01:41:37,857
在我把它們拿給你之前
Before I go just handing them over，

1473
01:41:37,859 --> 01:41:39,273
你必須答應我兩個條件
I do have one or two conditions. 

1474
01:41:39,409 --> 01:41:40,439
說
Name them. 

1475
01:41:40,441 --> 01:41:41,468
第一個
Firstly，

1476
01:41:41,611 --> 01:41:42,794
把羅盤還給我
I'll be having me compass back. 

1477
01:41:42,796 --> 01:41:43,977
不，那是第二個
No，no，that's secondly. 

1478
01:41:44,114 --> 01:41:46,378
第一個，你發誓
Firstly，upon your word，

1479
01:41:46,483 --> 01:41:48,474
不傷害安潔莉卡
you will bring no harm to Angelica. 

1480
01:41:48,618 --> 01:41:50,984
史派洛，我不會向你這種人發誓
I'll make no vows to the likes of you，Sparrow. 

1481
01:41:51,121 --> 01:41:53,589
不過答應你不傷害她
But it costs me nothing to admit

1482
01:41:53,723 --> 01:41:56,590
對我沒有損失
that she was never in harm's way. 

1483
01:41:57,227 --> 01:41:59,422
第二個，比第一個重要
Secondly then，priorly firstly，

1484
01:41:59,563 --> 01:42:01,190
把羅盤還給我
I will be having me compass back. 

1485
01:42:02,099 --> 01:42:04,124
拜託啦？那是我應得的
Please？I do deserve it. 

1486
01:42:04,267 --> 01:42:06,013
你知道那臭豬
Do you have any idea how difficult 

1487
01:42:06,014 --> 01:42:07,759
有多難綁嗎？
it was to catch that filthy pig？

1488
01:42:07,904 --> 01:42:09,087
不是兩條腿的
Not the big one，

1489
01:42:09,088 --> 01:42:10,270
是那四條腿的
the four-legged one. 

1490
01:42:13,710 --> 01:42:14,965
謝謝妳
Thank you. 

1491
01:42:14,966 --> 01:42:16,221
第三個
And thirdly，

1492
01:42:16,222 --> 01:42:17,476
黑鬍子先生
Mr. Beard，

1493
01:42:17,614 --> 01:42:20,449
有時候呀，不是常常
there are times，not very often，

1494
01:42:20,450 --> 01:42:23,544
在反省我的滔天罪行時
when I do reflect upon my heinous misdeeds. 

1495
01:42:23,720 --> 01:42:25,453
最惡劣的
Chief among them，

1496
01:42:25,454 --> 01:42:27,986
是我對待吉卜先生的態度
I note how poorly I have treated Mr. Gibbs，

1497
01:42:28,125 --> 01:42:29,456
我忠心耿耿的大副
my loyal first mate. 

1498
01:42:29,458 --> 01:42:30,787
對啊！現在你才想到...
Aye！Now you bring it up...

1499
01:42:30,927 --> 01:42:32,719
留下他在監獄裡腐爛
Left him to rot in jail，I did. 

1500
01:42:32,720 --> 01:42:33,623
我不在乎
Didn't care. 

1501
01:42:33,763 --> 01:42:35,318
現在還是不在乎
Still don't. 

1502
01:42:35,319 --> 01:42:36,873
但，這次
But，point being，

1503
01:42:36,874 --> 01:42:38,427
你必須放過他
you must let him go free. 

1504
01:42:40,270 --> 01:42:41,954
就這些？
Is that it？

1505
01:42:41,956 --> 01:42:43,637
我想是的
I think so. 

1506
01:42:43,773 --> 01:42:45,141
快決定，豬要是跑了
Quick，or the pig runs，

1507
01:42:45,142 --> 01:42:46,509
祝好運找到聖盃
and good luck getting those chalices. 

1508
01:42:46,510 --> 01:42:48,110
傑克，如果我是你，我一定...
Jack，if it's all the same to you，I'd be just as...

1509
01:42:48,111 --> 01:42:49,442
同意
Done. 

1510
01:42:49,546 --> 01:42:50,774
放了那頭豬
Release the swine. 

1511
01:42:56,553 --> 01:42:58,186
如果，你們不介意
Perhaps，if you don't mind，

1512
01:42:58,187 --> 01:42:59,818
我想跟著去...
I could tag along with you folk for a...

1513
01:43:02,559 --> 01:43:04,823
老兄，這會指引你奔向自由
This will lead you to freedom，mate. 

1514
01:43:11,501 --> 01:43:12,935
我發誓
I could have swore 

1515
01:43:12,936 --> 01:43:14,368
青春之泉就在這附近
it was somewhere right around here. 

1516
01:44:44,461 --> 01:44:46,827
我們不能停下
We must not stop. 

1517
01:45:04,147 --> 01:45:05,580
死路
Dead end. 

1518
01:45:06,583 --> 01:45:08,517
死路
Dead. End. 

1519
01:45:09,219 --> 01:45:10,618
死路
Dead end. 

1520
01:45:11,655 --> 01:45:13,540
傑克，我覺得
Jack，I'm starting to think  

1521
01:45:13,541 --> 01:45:15,424
你不知道地點
you don't know where you're going. 

1522
01:45:15,425 --> 01:45:18,258
俗話說，重要的是旅程不是結果
It is not the destination so much as the journey，they say. 

1523
01:45:19,462 --> 01:45:20,929
聖盃，拜託
Chalices，if you please. 

1524
01:45:32,942 --> 01:45:34,466
後退
Stand back. 

1525
01:45:56,833 --> 01:45:58,391
傑克...
Jack...

1526
01:45:58,535 --> 01:46:00,469
...你有沒有，真的...
...have you ever，in fact...

1527
01:46:00,603 --> 01:46:03,351
...親眼見到
...seen with your own eyes

1528
01:46:03,352 --> 01:46:06,098
...青春之泉？
...the Fountain of Youth？

1529
01:46:06,276 --> 01:46:08,437
抱歉，請重複妳的問題？
I'm sorry，could you repeat the question，please？

1530
01:46:08,611 --> 01:46:10,078
舵手
Quartermaster. 

1531
01:46:11,014 --> 01:46:11,981
不！
No，no！

1532
01:46:15,652 --> 01:46:17,779
等等！
Wait，wait！Wait. 

1533
01:46:21,057 --> 01:46:25,517
「生命...之水」
「Aqua...de Vida.」

1534
01:47:04,868 --> 01:47:07,393
石頭先生...
Master Scrum...

1535
01:47:07,537 --> 01:47:08,971
...可不可以？
...do you mind？

1536
01:47:08,973 --> 01:47:10,404
閣下？
Squire？

1537
01:48:09,098 --> 01:48:11,089
真漂亮
So beautiful. 

1538
01:48:50,573 --> 01:48:53,201
史派洛，我是第一個喝的
Sparrow，I'll be the first to taste those waters. 

1539
01:48:57,680 --> 01:48:59,272
父親
Father. 

1540
01:49:02,552 --> 01:49:04,850
獨腿人
The one-legged man. 

1541
01:49:07,390 --> 01:49:09,370
你把他帶來這裡
You brought him here. 

1542
01:49:09,372 --> 01:49:11,349
我會這麼做？
Would I do that？

1543
01:49:11,494 --> 01:49:13,587
愛德華汀奇！
Edward Teach！

1544
01:49:13,730 --> 01:49:17,029
對於你在公海上犯下的罪行
For crimes committed on the high seas，

1545
01:49:17,166 --> 01:49:21,034
奉國王陛下之名授予我的權力...
by the authority granted me by His Majesty the King...

1546
01:49:21,170 --> 01:49:24,367
...以及個人滿意的優厚條件...
...and with a goodly amount of personal satisfaction...

1547
01:49:24,507 --> 01:49:27,567
...依法逮捕你
...I hereby place you in the custody of the court，

1548
01:49:27,710 --> 01:49:31,043
你現在是我的犯人了
and declare you to be my prisoner. 

1549
01:49:32,081 --> 01:49:35,608
我的路到盡頭了，是這麼說吧？
My trick's out，is that it？

1550
01:49:35,752 --> 01:49:40,189
你犯的罪行包括有，海盜罪，叛國罪
Such crimes do include，but are not limited to，piracy，treason，

1551
01:49:40,290 --> 01:49:44,454
謀殺罪，最可惡的酷刑罪
murder，torture of the most heinous sort，

1552
01:49:44,594 --> 01:49:48,530
還有殘忍剝奪別人右腿罪
including the brutal theft of one used，twisted，hairy right leg. 

1553
01:49:49,299 --> 01:49:53,998
你...敢不敢面對這把劍？
You... dare face this sword？

1554
01:49:54,170 --> 01:49:56,604
離你的船這麼遠？當然敢
This far away from your ship？Aye. 

1555
01:49:56,739 --> 01:50:01,472
我感到命運冷酷的氣息在我頸後
Aye. That be the cold breath of fate I feel down my nape. 

1556
01:50:01,611 --> 01:50:07,277
以上帝之名，我會和你決一死鬥
But I'll have one last fight，by God. 

1557
01:50:07,417 --> 01:50:09,146
殺了他們！
Kill 'em all！

1558
01:50:10,787 --> 01:50:12,584
等一下
Hang on a minute. 

1559
01:50:12,722 --> 01:50:14,024
我只是...
I just... 

1560
01:50:14,025 --> 01:50:16,624
我只是想搞清楚一些事
I just need to understand something. 

1561
01:50:16,759 --> 01:50:18,443
來到這
Right，so，

1562
01:50:18,444 --> 01:50:20,126
你們要打他們
you will fight against them，

1563
01:50:20,263 --> 01:50:21,594
他們要打你們
they will fight against you. 

1564
01:50:21,731 --> 01:50:25,428
就因為他的腿被他砍了？
All on account of him wanting to kill him？

1565
01:50:25,568 --> 01:50:27,536
這什麼邏輯？
Where is the sense？

1566
01:50:27,537 --> 01:50:29,504
我沒說錯吧
Exactly. 

1567
01:50:29,639 --> 01:50:32,241
這樣吧，讓他們單挑
I say，let them fight each other， 

1568
01:50:32,242 --> 01:50:35,261
我們別插手，邊看，邊喝酒
while we lay back，watch，have a drink，

1569
01:50:35,262 --> 01:50:36,979
順便賭賭輸贏！
place some wagers！

1570
01:50:38,081 --> 01:50:39,378
好
Aye. 

1571
01:50:41,951 --> 01:50:42,765
殺了他們！
Kill 'em！

1572
01:50:42,767 --> 01:50:43,578
不留餘地！
No quarter！

1573
01:51:14,050 --> 01:51:15,711
滾開！
Get off me！

1574
01:51:48,685 --> 01:51:49,709
石頭，聖盃！
Scrum，the chalices！

1575
01:51:51,854 --> 01:51:52,980
還有人魚淚水！跟我來！
And the tear！Follow！

1576
01:51:56,993 --> 01:51:58,187
殺呀！
Fight！

1577
01:51:59,095 --> 01:52:00,282
拿過來
Hand it over. 

1578
01:52:00,283 --> 01:52:02,656
人魚淚水，這才是好樣的
The tear. There's a good lad.

1579
01:52:02,765 --> 01:52:05,097
比起怕你，我更怕她
I'm more afraid of her than I am of you. 

1580
01:52:10,640 --> 01:52:13,040
拿過來，這才是好樣的
Hand it over. There's a good lad. 

1581
01:52:16,412 --> 01:52:18,278
聖盃，拜託
The chalices，if you please. 

1582
01:52:18,280 --> 01:52:20,143
傑克，抱歉
Sorry，Jack. 

1583
01:52:20,316 --> 01:52:22,432
我跟你說過，我需要歲月
I told you，I need years. 

1584
01:52:22,434 --> 01:52:24,548
現在，你的就行了
And now，yours will do. 

1585
01:52:32,462 --> 01:52:33,690
石頭！
Scrum！

1586
01:52:55,351 --> 01:52:56,818
莎琳娜...
Syrena...

1587
01:53:00,556 --> 01:53:03,320
主啊，你不能帶她走
Oh God，you will not take her. 

1588
01:53:03,459 --> 01:53:05,939
如果你帶走了她
If you have taken her，

1589
01:53:05,941 --> 01:53:08,419
請讓她回來
you will give her back. 

1590
01:53:08,564 --> 01:53:10,930
讓她回來...
Give her back...

1591
01:53:11,067 --> 01:53:13,934
讓她回來，求求?
Give her back，please. Please. 

1592
01:53:37,527 --> 01:53:40,291
我以為命運會眷顧你，嗯？
I expected fate to put up more of a fight，eh？

1593
01:53:57,146 --> 01:53:59,046
是我被擊倒的話
I will not have that smile on your face 

1594
01:53:59,047 --> 01:54:00,946
我肯定笑不出來
as I strike you down. 

1595
01:54:02,351 --> 01:54:05,445
愛德華汀奇，轉頭看吧
Take a gander，Edward Teach. 

1596
01:54:35,985 --> 01:54:39,284
這塊土地永遠屬於光榮的
This land is hereby forever claimed in the glorious name

1597
01:54:39,455 --> 01:54:42,015
喬治王陛下名下...
of His Majesty King George...

1598
01:54:48,264 --> 01:54:51,199
你的勇敢將載入史冊
Someone make a note of that man's bravery. 

1599
01:54:58,174 --> 01:55:01,905
小姐，聖盃，請拿給我
Senorita，the chalices，por favor. 

1600
01:55:18,594 --> 01:55:21,427
只有上帝能賜予永生
Only God can grant eternal life，

1601
01:55:21,429 --> 01:55:24,260
不是這個異教之泉
not this pagan water. 

1602
01:55:35,311 --> 01:55:38,803
摧毀這座異教寺院！
Men，destroy this profane temple！

1603
01:55:41,550 --> 01:55:42,881
青春之泉！
The Fountain！

1604
01:55:56,933 --> 01:55:58,457
你是個笨蛋
You are a fool. 

1605
01:55:58,601 --> 01:56:00,251
你在這奡M找的
You seek in this place what 

1606
01:56:00,252 --> 01:56:01,900
只有信仰才能給你
only faith can provide. 

1607
01:56:02,004 --> 01:56:03,284
信仰？
Faith？

1608
01:56:03,285 --> 01:56:04,673
的確，可以光明的讓你看見
In faith，there is light enough to see

1609
01:56:04,674 --> 01:56:06,938
但也可以黑暗的讓你失明
but darkness enough to blind. 

1610
01:56:10,546 --> 01:56:12,810
這是什麼妖術？
What devilry is this？

1611
01:56:16,786 --> 01:56:18,083
這是為了鬼盜船
For the Pearl. 

1612
01:56:18,085 --> 01:56:19,380
你做了什麼？
What have you done？

1613
01:56:22,925 --> 01:56:25,325
安潔莉卡！不要！劍有毒！
Angelica！Don't！It's poison！

1614
01:56:29,966 --> 01:56:32,298
我不會傻到沒有一點優勢
I'm not such the fool to take on Blackbeard

1615
01:56:32,435 --> 01:56:35,836
就來抓黑鬍子的
without a little venomous advantage. 

1616
01:56:37,139 --> 01:56:38,629
傑克！
Jack！

1617
01:56:50,453 --> 01:56:52,652
我宣佈黑鬍子的船和船員
I claim Blackbeard's ship and crew，

1618
01:56:52,655 --> 01:56:54,373
以及這把劍
and this sword，

1619
01:56:54,374 --> 01:56:56,091
賠償我失去的腿！
payment for my missing limb！

1620
01:57:10,506 --> 01:57:11,905
抓好了！拉！
Hang on！Pull！

1621
01:57:57,186 --> 01:57:59,552
別浪費了我的淚水
Do not waste my tear. 

1622
01:58:29,018 --> 01:58:30,082
喝下這杯
Drink this. 

1623
01:58:30,083 --> 01:58:31,145
這杯有人魚淚水
This one has the tear. 

1624
01:58:31,287 --> 01:58:32,283
你必須喝另一杯
You must drink the other. 

1625
01:58:32,285 --> 01:58:33,278
不！
No！

1626
01:58:34,056 --> 01:58:35,672
你們倆沒法同時救
I cannot save you both. 

1627
01:58:35,674 --> 01:58:37,287
你們得犧牲一個
One of you must sacrifice. 

1628
01:58:38,227 --> 01:58:41,321
你喝吧，父親，救贖你的靈魂
You take it，Father，for your soul. 

1629
01:58:43,365 --> 01:58:46,084
汀奇船長，她快死了
Captain Teach，she's dying. 

1630
01:58:46,086 --> 01:58:48,803
你得救你的女兒
You must save your daughter. 

1631
01:58:49,972 --> 01:58:52,770
這杯是死？
This one takes life？

1632
01:58:52,908 --> 01:58:54,773
這杯是生？
This one has the tear and gives life？

1633
01:58:54,910 --> 01:58:56,172
對，快喝啊！
Aye，hurry！

1634
01:59:05,087 --> 01:59:09,353
安潔莉卡...我的女兒，救救我
Angelica...Save me，my child. 

1635
01:59:11,260 --> 01:59:12,693
不
No. 

1636
01:59:21,403 --> 01:59:22,836
父親，我愛你
I love you，Father. 

1637
01:59:35,818 --> 01:59:37,445
等等
Wait a minute. 

1638
01:59:39,622 --> 01:59:42,455
我好像弄反了
In fact，it might have been the other way around. 

1639
01:59:43,292 --> 01:59:45,209
這杯才有淚水
This cup had the tear，

1640
01:59:45,210 --> 01:59:47,126
你喝的那杯沒有
that one had the other bit. 

1641
01:59:47,229 --> 01:59:48,491
騙子！
Trickster！

1642
01:59:48,631 --> 01:59:49,564
惡魔！
Devil！

1643
01:59:49,566 --> 01:59:50,496
父親！
Father！

1644
01:59:57,506 --> 01:59:59,099
混蛋！你怎麼可以這樣？
You bastard！How could you？

1645
02:00:00,042 --> 02:00:01,643
妳的父親救了妳
Your father saved you. 

1646
02:00:01,644 --> 02:00:04,169
也許他的靈魂得到救贖了，嗯？
Perhaps his soul is now redeemed，eh？

1647
02:01:04,974 --> 02:01:07,101
你受傷了
You are hurt. 

1648
02:01:09,311 --> 02:01:11,245
只是肉體
In body only. 

1649
02:01:12,915 --> 02:01:15,031
我的心靈很平靜...
My mind is at peace...

1650
02:01:15,032 --> 02:01:17,147
因為妳
because of you. 

1651
02:01:18,220 --> 02:01:19,654
我？
Me？

1652
02:01:19,656 --> 02:01:21,087
對
Yes. 

1653
02:01:22,091 --> 02:01:24,491
我曾經迷失
I was lost. 

1654
02:01:25,461 --> 02:01:30,125
海風，潮汐...
The wind，the tides...

1655
02:01:30,266 --> 02:01:33,326
...它們應該可以使人恢復信仰
...they ought to renew a man's faith. 

1656
02:01:34,903 --> 02:01:36,837
但使我恢復信仰的，只有妳
But for me，only you. 

1657
02:01:37,740 --> 02:01:41,471
菲利浦，我可以救你
Philip，I can save you. 

1658
02:01:41,610 --> 02:01:44,579
只要你要求我
You need only ask. 

1659
02:01:46,015 --> 02:01:48,416
我只要求一件事
I seek but one thing. 

1660
02:01:48,418 --> 02:01:50,816
什麼事？
What is that？

1661
02:01:51,820 --> 02:01:54,186
寬恕
Forgiveness. 

1662
02:01:54,323 --> 02:01:55,990
要不是我
If not for me，

1663
02:01:55,991 --> 02:01:57,656
妳不會被抓住
you would never have been captured. 

1664
02:01:57,793 --> 02:01:59,454
要求吧
Ask. 

1665
02:02:01,330 --> 02:02:03,161
原諒我？
Forgive me？

1666
02:02:28,290 --> 02:02:29,518
我恨你
I hate you. 

1667
02:02:29,658 --> 02:02:31,990
救過妳命的笨蛋？
The bloke who saved your life？

1668
02:02:32,127 --> 02:02:33,726
我擁有的歲月
The years I possess，

1669
02:02:33,727 --> 02:02:35,324
偷竊自我的父親！
stolen from my own father！

1670
02:02:35,464 --> 02:02:36,977
我只是幫黑鬍子
I only helped Blackbeard do what 

1671
02:02:36,978 --> 02:02:38,490
盡了父親該做的事
any father should have done. 

1672
02:02:38,634 --> 02:02:41,831
你既殘忍又無知
You are cruel and ignorant. 

1673
02:02:45,541 --> 02:02:49,341
一把手槍，一顆子彈
One pistol，one shot. 

1674
02:02:49,478 --> 02:02:51,708
在我餓死前自殺？
To kill myself before I starve？

1675
02:02:51,847 --> 02:02:53,405
親愛的，我信不過妳
There's no trusting you，love. 

1676
02:02:53,549 --> 02:02:56,017
再說，這是繁忙的貿易路線
Besides，this is a well-traveled trade route. 

1677
02:02:56,151 --> 02:02:57,743
妳可以給經過的船隻打信號
You can signal a passing ship. 

1678
02:02:57,886 --> 02:03:01,344
或者妳可以飲彈自盡，隨妳便
Or you can just bite the proverbial bullet，as it were. 

1679
02:03:01,490 --> 02:03:03,082
那我又要怎麼掙脫這些繩索？
And how will I get free of these bonds？

1680
02:03:03,225 --> 02:03:05,989
半個小時前妳就掙脫繩索了
You broke free of your bonds half an hour ago，

1681
02:03:06,095 --> 02:03:08,928
正在想著怎麼樣向我發動襲擊
waiting for the precise moment to pounce. 

1682
02:03:11,633 --> 02:03:13,328
傑克，承認吧
Admit it，Jack. 

1683
02:03:13,435 --> 02:03:15,403
你還愛著我
You still love me. 

1684
02:03:15,405 --> 02:03:17,371
如果你有妹妹和一隻狗
If you had a sister and a dog，

1685
02:03:17,506 --> 02:03:19,804
我會選擇那隻狗
I'd choose the dog. 

1686
02:03:19,975 --> 02:03:23,342
寶藏！有個裝滿珠寶的箱子！
Treasure！There is a chest with jewels！

1687
02:03:23,445 --> 02:03:25,709
珠寶擁有控制風向和潮汐的力量！
Jewels with the power to rule the wind and tide！

1688
02:03:25,848 --> 02:03:27,395
妳在亂掰！
You're making that up！

1689
02:03:27,397 --> 02:03:28,942
等等...
Wait...

1690
02:03:29,752 --> 02:03:31,601
我懷孕了
I am with child. 

1691
02:03:31,602 --> 02:03:33,449
是你的
Yours. 

1692
02:03:34,690 --> 02:03:36,089
我不記得我們有過...
I don't recall that we ever had...

1693
02:03:36,225 --> 02:03:37,590
那次你喝醉了！
You were drunk！

1694
02:03:37,592 --> 02:03:38,955
我從沒醉到那種程度
I've actually never been that drunk. 

1695
02:03:39,094 --> 02:03:40,220
等等！
Wait！

1696
02:03:42,097 --> 02:03:44,156
我有些話想對你說
There is something I want to say to you. 

1697
02:03:44,333 --> 02:03:48,497
從一見面起我就想說
Something I wanted to say from the moment we first met. 

1698
02:03:49,438 --> 02:03:50,564
說吧
Go on，then. 

1699
02:03:52,908 --> 02:03:54,239
我愛你
I love you. 

1700
02:03:57,813 --> 02:03:59,644
我也愛妳
As do I. 

1701
02:03:59,782 --> 02:04:01,511
永遠都愛
Always have. 

1702
02:04:01,512 --> 02:04:03,240
永遠不變
Always will. 

1703
02:04:07,756 --> 02:04:09,246
我得走了
I gotta go. 

1704
02:04:09,391 --> 02:04:10,415
傑克！
Jack！

1705
02:04:12,728 --> 02:04:14,320
我跟你還沒完！
This is not over！

1706
02:04:15,397 --> 02:04:16,455
傑克！
Jack！

1707
02:04:26,041 --> 02:04:27,531
打偏啦！
Missed！

1708
02:04:42,825 --> 02:04:45,851
這個「復仇」屬於我
The Revenge is mine. 

1709
02:04:52,534 --> 02:04:54,001
先生...
Sir...

1710
02:04:56,472 --> 02:04:58,337
我們在甲板下發現這個
We found this below decks. 

1711
02:05:24,433 --> 02:05:26,697
全體船員！迎風航行！
All hands！Ply to windward！

1712
02:05:26,835 --> 02:05:30,396
揚起船帆，你們這些蟑螂！
Get cracking，ye blooming cockroaches！

1713
02:05:33,108 --> 02:05:35,702
雖然國王待我不薄
The Crown served me well. 

1714
02:05:35,844 --> 02:05:38,836
不過現在，以海神及天神之名...
But now，by the gods of sea and sky...

1715
02:05:38,981 --> 02:05:43,077
...向龜島全速前進！
...make way for Tortuga！

1716
02:05:54,196 --> 02:05:56,305
吉卜，你這邪惡，糊塗的醉鬼
Gibbs，you filthy，besotted shellback

1717
02:05:56,307 --> 02:05:57,359
你搞定啦！
you made it！

1718
02:05:57,499 --> 02:05:59,057
對啊！
Aye！

1719
02:05:59,201 --> 02:06:00,793
我相信我們聯手
And I trust we managed a profit

1720
02:06:00,936 --> 02:06:03,018
成功了是不是？
from our joint enterprise？

1721
02:06:03,020 --> 02:06:05,100
睜亮你的眼睛
Feast your eyes. 

1722
02:06:10,178 --> 02:06:12,703
羅盤指引我的方向很正確
The compass led me straight and true. 

1723
02:06:12,848 --> 02:06:14,839
那黑鬍子看船的手下呢？
What of Blackbeard's men guarding the ship？

1724
02:06:14,950 --> 02:06:18,852
我用新幾內亞的絕招擺平了
I employed the selfsame maneuver we perfected in New Guinea. 

1725
02:06:18,954 --> 02:06:23,050
沒弄走全部艦隊有點可惜
Seemed a shame to leave an entire fleet behind. 

1726
02:06:23,191 --> 02:06:25,250
是有點可惜
Shame indeed. 

1727
02:06:37,205 --> 02:06:38,570
我討厭那隻猴子
I hate that monkey. 

1728
02:06:38,707 --> 02:06:42,143
鬼盜船...要怎樣把她弄出來？
So，the Pearl...Any idea how to get her out？

1729
02:06:42,277 --> 02:06:43,790
需要一把十字弓
We shall need a crossbow，

1730
02:06:43,791 --> 02:06:45,303
一個砂時計，三隻山羊
an hourglass，three goats. 

1731
02:06:45,447 --> 02:06:46,960
一人唸咒語同時
One of us must learn to play the trumpet whilst 

1732
02:06:46,962 --> 02:06:48,473
另一人裝神弄鬼...
the other one goes like this...

1733
02:06:48,984 --> 02:06:50,634
我認識一個有山羊的人
I know a man with a goat. 

1734
02:06:50,636 --> 02:06:52,283
你把山羊弄來，我擅長裝神弄鬼
Good. I can go like this. 

1735
02:06:54,923 --> 02:06:56,584
傑克，我不明白...
Jack，I have to ask...

1736
02:06:56,725 --> 02:06:58,159
你有了聖盃
You had the chalices，

1737
02:06:58,160 --> 02:06:59,592
青春之泉，人魚淚水...
the water，the tear...

1738
02:06:59,728 --> 02:07:02,253
你大可以擁有永生的
You could have lived maybe forever. 

1739
02:07:02,397 --> 02:07:04,365
青春之泉是一個考驗，吉卜
The Fountain does test you，Gibbs. 

1740
02:07:04,533 --> 02:07:05,784
永遠不要妄圖知道
But better to not know  

1741
02:07:05,785 --> 02:07:07,434
自己的生命終點
which moment may be your last. 

1742
02:07:07,569 --> 02:07:09,594
生命的奧義
Every morsel of your entire being

1743
02:07:09,738 --> 02:07:12,832
就是活在當下
alive to the infinite mystery of it all. 

1744
02:07:12,975 --> 02:07:15,500
誰說我就不能永生，嗯？
And who's to say I won't live forever，eh？

1745
02:07:15,644 --> 02:07:18,772
我是青春之泉的發現者耶
Discoverer of the Fountain of Youth. 

1746
02:07:18,914 --> 02:07:21,815
我本身就成為一個傳奇了，吉卜
I have no say in it，Gibbs. 

1747
02:07:21,950 --> 02:07:23,941
我是個不折不扣的海盜
It's a pirate's life for me. 

1748
02:07:24,886 --> 02:07:26,376
了了？
Savvy？

